apps.title: Bolt Food
apps.description:
Craving something delicious? Whether it's pizza, tacos, or your favourite fast food from Burger King and KFC, Bolt Food delivers straight to your door.

WHY CHOOSE BOLT FOOD?
- Real-time tracking: track your order and courier’s location from the restaurant to your doorstep.
- Convenient scheduling: plan ahead and order food or groceries in advance.
- Pickup options: prefer to grab your meal yourself? Use our pickup feature for easy collections.
- Takeaway deals and discounts: save on your favourite meals and snacks.
- Seamless payments: pay effortlessly using Google Pay, Apple Pay, or credit/debit cards.

HOW TO GET STARTED:
1. Set your delivery address.
2. Browse and pick meals, groceries, or snacks from your favourite local restaurants or stores.
3. Place your food order and pay securely.
4. Track your order in real-time.
5. Sit back and enjoy!

DISCOVER LOCAL AND GLOBAL FAVOURITES:
Explore a culinary world at your fingertips with Bolt Food. From beloved local restaurants to renowned fast food chains like McDonald's, get meals from your favourite restaurants delivered to your door.

*BOLT MARKET - QUICK GROCERY DELIVERY:
Need groceries or essentials delivered? Bolt Market brings everyday items like milk, bread, and coffee, as well as speciality products like pet supplies, cosmetics, or alcohol, right to your doorstep. Forget the long supermarket queues and shop smarter with Bolt Market.

*BOLT PLUS
With Bolt Plus, you can access exclusive benefits that save you time and money. For example, you can enjoy priority delivery for your orders, even during the busiest hours.

*GO OUT AND SAVE WITH DINEOUT
As convenient as it is to get food delivered to your door, some moments are worth making the trip out for. Find tables at nearby DineOut restaurants and get a discount off your meal. Just open the app, search for what you crave, and switch to the DineOut tab for in-restaurant offers. 

Bolt Food was created by the European super-app Bolt. It’s challenging the efficiency of the food and grocery delivery industry while helping restaurants and stores get more orders and enabling couriers to earn money.

Become a Bolt Food Courier partner:
Have a car, bike, or motorbike? Earn money delivering meals with Bolt Food: https://bolt.eu/en/food/courier/.

Partner with Bolt Food:
Are you a restaurant or grocery store? Boost your sales by joining Bolt Food: https://bolt.eu/en/food/partner/.

Get in touch with us via food@bolt.eu

Follow us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/boltfood.

- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
*Only available in selected markets.

apps.title: Favor: Texas Food Delivery
apps.description:
Favor is the delivery app made by Texans, for Texans. From an extra-hot latte that meets you at the office to queso delivered (almost) right to your couch, we’re here when y’all are hungry.

Texans’ must-have membership
- Subscribe to the best of Texas with Favor Gold! Packed with uniquely local savings and perks, it’s everything you love about Texas, made even better.
- Members enjoy unlimited $0 delivery fees on almost everything in the app, monthly H-E-B savings, discounts for supporting local, reduced service fees, and much more.
- Try Favor Gold and enjoy 30 days free for a limited time!

PROUDLY PART OF H-E-B
- Experience the quality, value, selection, and service you expect from H-E-B in every single delivery.
- Available exclusively in the Favor app, H-E-B Now is the easiest way to get last-minute groceries right when you need them.
- Get restaurants for when you’re hungry now and groceries for when you’re hungry later—all in one place. Update to the latest version of the app to shop H-E-B Now and all your other in-store favorites!
- Delivery fees are always $0 from H-E-B-owned restaurants and stores, including H-E-B Beer & Wine, True Texas BBQ, and Blooms by H-E-B!
- H-E-B Visa® cardholders also earn unlimited 5% cash back on every Favor order. 

THOUSANDS OF RESTAURANTS AND STORES
- Get the best selection of national and Texas-only restaurants—plus alcohol, flowers, and more—delivered in as little as 45 minutes.
- Support locally-owned businesses and give back to your community.
- Order from favorites like Burger King, McDonald’s, Buffalo Wild Wings, Papa John’s Pizza, Applebee’s, Whataburger, Panda Express, Church’s Chicken, Five Guys, Dairy Queen, California Pizza Kitchen, Firehouse Subs, Hooters, Jersey Mike’s Subs, Pei Wei, Romano’s Macaroni Grill, Urban Bricks Pizza, Velvet Taco, Zoës Kitchen, and more!

DELIVERY YOU CAN HANG YOUR HAT ON
- We’re committed to making sure your order is fresh, accurate, and on time (every time).

TRULY TEXAN HOSPITALITY 
- We’ll always treat your order with care because we’re food lovers who just happen to be food deliverers.
- Enjoy one-on-one service and personal updates from your Runner (that’s what we call Favor delivery drivers).

PROUDLY UNAVAILABLE IN 49 STATES
- As a homegrown Texas brand and part of the H-E-B family, we’re uniquely focused on serving fellow Texans in more than 400 cities across the Lone Star State.
- Abilene, Arlington, Austin, Baytown, Beaumont, Brownsville, College Station, Corpus Christi, Dallas, Denton, Fort Worth, Georgetown, Houston, Killeen, Lubbock, Midland, New Braunfels, Odessa, Port Arthur, San Antonio, San Marcos, Temple, and Waco are just a few of them!

5-STAR SUPPORT
- Want real help from a real person? Our Texas-based team is ready to assist you throughout your delivery experience.

The H-E-B Visa Signature® Credit Card is issued by First Electronic Bank, Member FDIC, pursuant to a license from Visa USA Inc. The H-E-B Credit Card is powered by Imprint Payments, Inc. See Rewards Program Terms and Conditions and Credit Program Cardholder Agreement on heb.com/credit.

apps.title: Zé Delivery de Bebidas
apps.developer: EMPRESARIOS DETALLISTAS DE MEXICO, S.A. DE C.V.
apps.description:
Delivery de bebidas: gelada, em minutos e entrega grátis no primeiro pedido!

Com o Zé Delivery, a bebida chega até você em minutos: sem fila e sem perrengue! Cervejas, destilados, vinhos, refrigerantes e muito mais, tudo no precinho, e o melhor: sempre gelada!

São mais de 100 milhões de pedidos entregues, sem sair de casa e em apenas alguns cliques:
1) Escolher endereço de entrega
2) Selecionar produtos: navegando por nossas categorias você encontra bebidas, petiscos, além de itens para seu churrasco, como carvão e gelo!
3) Escolher forma de pagamento: você pode pagar online ou na entrega

Com o Zé Delivery, é possível economizar tempo e dinheiro, evitando o perrengue de sair de casa, pegar trânsito, enfrentar fila e carregar peso para garantir sua bebida!

Aqui você garante tudo o que precisa para aproveitar os melhores momentos com amigos e família: seja no churrasco, no esquenta, durante aquela partida do seu time do coração ou até pra relaxar em casa.

Por que escolher o Zé Delivery?
- Entrega rápida: em minutos, a bebida chega gelada.
- Preço baixo: a melhor opção para cerveja, vinhos, destilados e mais.
- Praticidade: sem sair de casa, sem enfrentar filas, sem carregar peso.
- Onde a gente entrega?

Nossos parceiros distribuidores estão em todos os estados do Brasil. Já são mais de 700 cidades atendidas! Confira a lista completa no nosso site https://www.ze.delivery/cidades-atendidas.

Se ainda não atendemos a sua cidade, pode mandar um e-mail para atendimento_ze@ambev.com.br contando onde você gostaria de receber seu pedido. Estamos crescendo e fazemos questão de chegar aí também.

- Dúvidas, elogios, reclamações, ombro amigo?
É só falar com a gente através do e-mail atendimento_ze@ambev.com.br. Nossa equipe está a postos todos os dias das 8h às 2h da manhã.

- Quer ser um parceiro e entregar bebidas através do Zé Delivery? Vale dar uma olhada em www.ze.delivery/partner.

apps.title: foodpanda: Food & Groceries
apps.description:
Discover the local choice for meals, groceries, and food delivery with foodpanda!

Life can get overwhelming, but we’re here to help! Whether you need daily meals, groceries, or shopping essentials, foodpanda has got you covered with convenient food delivery.

Order Your Favourite Food with Just 3 Simple Taps!

With foodpanda, you can easily choose the food you love, and we’ll deliver it right to your door. Serving millions across over 400 cities in 11 Asian markets — Singapore, Hong Kong, Thailand, Malaysia, Pakistan, Taiwan, the Philippines, Bangladesh, Laos, Cambodia, and Myanmar — foodpanda is your go-to for everyday food delivery.

Endless Food and Grocery Delivery Choices at Your Fingertips!
Hungry for wood-fired pizza, a classic burger or fried chicken? We know the best restaurants near you – big famous brands and tiny local faves. Best part? We've got exclusive discounts and promos waiting for all new foodies. With a simple click, your food and groceries are on their way with fast delivery!

Need Groceries? We’ve Got You Covered!
Want to cook but short on time? Imagine having fresh produce, pantry staples, frozen goods, personal care items, your cute pets' needs, and much more, delivered in a flash — everything you need for a hassle-free home-cooked meal, all available through our speedy groceries delivery service from foodpanda shops and pandamarts.

Best Food and Grocery Delivery Deals Just for You!
Looking for the best savings on groceries and food? We regularly update our daily deals, personalised just for you! Here’s a tip: skip the queue and choose self pick-up for extra savings on your grocery orders, or enjoy the convenience of our food delivery options.

Save on tasty takeaways.
On the go? Try pick-up! Skip the queue and save up when you self-collect your order.

Worry-free package delivery.
Need to send or receive a parcel? Go with pandago. Our reliable fleet and on-demand delivery service will safely deliver it for you in no time.

Our tech is shaped by you.
Explore personalised offers and delicious picks just for you. Dish out what you feel about your order and let foodies know what’s yum. 

Want More? Join pandapro!
Unlock even greater savings on food delivery and grocery options with our pandapro membership today!

Live like a panda and let us take care of the rest — let’s do it the panda way with seamless food delivery!

For more info, please visit our website.

apps.title: 7NOW: Food & Drinks Delivery
apps.description:
Why You’ll Love 7NOW:
You can now use your SNAP EBT card to pay for eligible items directly in the app. SNAP covers approved food items only and can’t be used for delivery fees, tips, or non-food products. Our updated checkout makes split payments easy — use SNAP for eligible items and another card for everything else. This update makes shopping smoother and more accessible than ever.
Available in select locations only.
7-Eleven Gold Pass™: Enjoy $0 delivery fees, discounted pricing for students, free drinks, 10% 7-Eleven Cash, and more. Sign up for a 30-day free trial today! 
5% 7-Eleven Cash: Get rewarded every time you order! Earn up to 10% cashback in 7-Eleven Cash on eligible purchases—and use it in-store or in-app.
Alcohol Delivery: Get your favorite drinks delivered right to your door. 
24/7 Fast Delivery: Craving something late at night? We’ve got you covered with super-fast delivery anytime, anywhere.
7NOW delivers all your favorites—food, alcohol, candy, snacks, drinks, ice cream, groceries, health needs, and more—in about 30 minutes.
Get 5% 7-Eleven Cash and save more on your eligible orders. Gold Pass Members earn 10% 7-Eleven Cash!
7-Eleven GOLD PASS™ 
Sign up for 7-Eleven Gold Pass and enjoy $0 delivery fees on all your favorite 7NOW products. Discounted pricing for students, free products, 10% 7-Eleven Cash, and tons of other perks. Sign up for a 30-day free trial today!
WHATEVER YOU WANT—DELIVERED
Choose from over 3000+ items and counting. We deliver alcohol, snacks, food, candy, health, school & office supplies straight to your location!
NEW! LOCAL RESTAURANT DELIVERY 
Got a craving for a local favorite? Introducing restaurant delivery! Enjoy your favorite restaurant meal delivered straight to your door.
24/7 DELIVERY IN 30 MINUTES 
Stay in the moment with worry-free delivery in about 30 minutes. Now that’s super-fast!
$7 OFF YOUR FIRST ORDER 
Use Promo code 711TREAT Get $7 off your first delivery purchase made through the 7NOW App. (Terms and conditions apply.)
REFER-A-FRIEND PROGRAM
Refer a friend and get a basket discount credit as soon as they place their first order on the 7NOW app. Terms and conditions apply.
ACTIVE IN MOST MAJOR US CITIES 
7NOW is available in over 200 cities across 43 metro areas! We’re adding new cities and locations all the time.
FLAT DELIVERY FEE 
We charge a flat, low delivery fee to make things easy and simple for you. Or sign up for Gold Pass and get unlimited FREE deliveries!
NO MINIMUMS 
Order as little or as much as you want. A nominal small basket fee may apply to orders less than $15.
PAYMENTS MADE EASY 
We accept all major credit and debit cards plus Apple Pay. All transactions are 100% digital, no need for cash.
REAL-TIME ORDER TRACKING

apps.title: Yango: taxi, food, delivery
apps.description:
Yango is an easy-to-use app for getting around the city
Fill your life with movement. Get the whole city in your hands, ride wherever you want, and enjoy comfort at an affordable price. With Yango, everything is possible!

Choose the right service class for you
Reach your destination at the right level of comfort and price for you. Choose from several service classes. Economy is awesome for when you need a ride fast. Comfort lets you sit back and just enjoy the ride. And The Fastest is the best in case when the service class doesn’t matter and you just need the closest ride available!

Ride safely
Safety is our top priority. You’ll see who’s coming to pick you up and in which car right in the app. You’ll see info about the driver, such as their name and rating, and will be able to share your route with whomever you like so they know where you are.

Smart destinations
Yango will suggest destinations for your rides based on your ride history, like first offering ‘home’ as a destination because it’s your most common request on weekday evenings. Ride the smart way!

Multiple destinations, one route
Yango makes everyday life super easy. Like picking the kids up from school, dropping a friend off at a market, and doing some quick shopping on the way. Just add a new stop in the app, and Yango will recalculate a new route for the driver. 

Request rides for close ones
Show you care by requesting rides for friends and relatives. Get your mother to a doctor’s appointment, book a ride to pick up your special someone, or get each of your friends a ride home after a night out. You can request up to 3 cars at once.

Refer friends and get discounts
Invite friends to try Yango and save together. Share your personal promo code, get a discount on your next ride and grant your friend with an extra discount on their first ride. It’s as easy as that.

Meet Delivery - it's like a taxi service, but for your packages

We've also built in a fast delivery service into Yango - use Delivery to quickly send personal packages or even business orders by courier anywhere in the city. Delivery is suitable for any item that can be transported by scooter or car. 

An international service
Yango is a ride-hailing, mobility, and delivery aggregator service that operates in more than 20 countries around the world, including Ghana, Cote d'Ivoire, Cameroon, Senegal and Zambia.

Yango is an informational service and not a transportation or taxi services provider. Transportation services are provided by third parties.
The size and duration of the discount for the first rides requested via the Yango app vary depending on the country and city. Open the app for specific details.

Privacy Policy:
https://yango.com/legal/yango_privacy_notice
Yango Plus subscription conditions:
https://deli.yango.com/en-IL/about/docs/legal/yango_plus_conditions

apps.title: Spoke (Circuit) Route Planner
apps.description:
Circuit Route Planner is now Spoke Route Planner. Same trusted app, just a new name.

Easy-to-use multi-stop route planner and delivery app downloaded by over 10 million drivers - Sign up for a FREE trial today!

Deliver more packages and finish your route faster. Save time, money, and gas with Circuit Route Planner.

Adding stops to a route takes seconds. A single click optimizes all your deliveries and automatically maps out the fastest routes. Avoid traffic, find packages quicker, and deliver more efficiently.

Using Spoke Route Planner, you can...
• Find and add stops easily using your keypad, voice, or Apple Live Text
• Add an unlimited number of deliveries and routes per day
• Avoid traffic and delays with a route planner that automatically maps the fastest routes
• Make last-minute changes to routes during the day
• Use it with your favorite GPS - Waze, Google Maps, Apple Maps, and more…
• Set delivery time windows and priority levels for specific stops
• Customize the amount of time to spend at each stop, and add rest breaks
• Get instant and accurate ETAs
• Add package details to make loading your truck and locating an item easier
And much more…

The top-choice route planning and delivery app for couriers and delivery drivers, used to deliver in over 190 countries. Helping drivers discover the best routes, avoid traffic, boost earnings, and finish ahead of schedule every day.

“I’m a courier and deliver about 150 packages a day. This route planner always gives me the fastest route, so I can deliver more packages in less time. I make more money and save around an hour a day using Spoke. It’s the best app of all the ones I’ve tried” - Nathan, Canada

Spoke Route Planner - Free
The free version of Spoke Route Planner gives you unlimited access to all features, but routes are limited to a maximum of 10 stops.

Spoke Route Planner - Lite
Spoke Route Planner Lite gives you an unlimited number of routes and stops, with restricted access to some features.

Spoke Route Planner - Standard
Spoke Route Planner Standard gives you unlimited access to all features and no restrictions on routes or stops.

7-day trial complete? Subscribe to the right plan for you and save time, money, and gas by using a delivery route planner that helps you do more and finish your route faster.

FAQs

Will Spoke Route Planner work in my country?
Spoke Route Planner works in almost every country because it uses location data provided by Google Maps. If Google Maps works where you live, then Spoke Route Planner will work for you. We have users in over 190 countries and on every continent.

Which languages does Spoke support?
Spoke will automatically use your phone language if it is supported. If it is not, it will default to US English

How many routes can I create?
You can have unlimited routes on the free and paid version of Spoke Route Planner

How many stops can I add to my route?
You can add up to ten stops per route on the free version of Spoke Route Planner.

How do I subscribe/cancel my subscription?
Subscriptions auto-renew monthly and are charged to your Apple account. Cancel anytime by turning off auto-renew in your Apple account 24 hours before the renewal date. Rates vary by country, and the local price for your region will be provided before you complete payment.

Support: https://help.spoke.com/en/collections/385293-spoke-for-individual-drivers
What’s new?: https://spoke.com/route-planner/product-updates
Terms of Service: https://spoke.com/terms
Privacy Policy: https://spoke.com/privacy

apps.title: Wonder: Food Delivery
apps.description:
Everything's on the menu. Except compromise. The Wonder app is the food delivery platform to feed every craving, all in one order. Combine dishes from our exclusive restaurant partners, spanning every cuisine you can think of and brought to you by the best chefs in the industry, get your favorite neighborhood gems delivered, or whip up a Blue Apron meal in minutes. Order on the app with free delivery or pickup and dine-in at our locations throughout the East Coast.
 
25+ AWARD-WINNING RESTAURANT PARTNERS
There’s an option for anything you’re craving, from Greek to Thai, with menus from world-famous chefs like Bobby Flay, José Andrés, and Marcus Samuelsson. 

MIX & MATCH HUNDREDS OF DISHES
Craving barbecue but they’re in the mood for tacos? Don’t compromise. Combine dishes from multiple menus in one order, they’ll be made to order and delivered together. 

$0 DELIVERY FEES—ALWAYS
Dine-in or pickup at any of our locations throughout the Northeast, or get your order delivered in minutes. At Wonder, delivery is free. 

FIND HUNDREDS OF RESTAURANTS NEAR YOU
Get fast local food delivery near you. Visit our Wonder locations across the East Coast for pickup and dine-in, or get free delivery from the best neighborhood spots on the app. 

BLUE APRON MEAL KITS
Feel like cooking tonight? Or only have a few minutes to spare? Order Blue Apron—America’s favorite meal kit—plus pre-made meals and more, on the Wonder app with no subscription needed. 

REAL-TIME TRACKING
Follow your delivery or takeout order every step of the way in the app and with text alerts. From your first tap on the app, to the moment you’re served warmly at your door. 

PAYMENTS
We accept all major credit cards, Apple Pay, and Google Pay. 

FOOD DELIVERY FOR ANYTHING YOU’RE CRAVING
Italian, pizza, steakhouse, sandwiches, burgers, seafood, poke, Thai, Greek, Middle Eastern, salads, Mexican, family-style, American, Chinese, barbecue, and more. 

Learn more at wonder.com.

Choose from many popular local restaurants and exclusive eateries you won't find on other delivery services -- from local mom-and-pop to Michelin-rated and The Infatuation picks!

apps.title: maxim: order a taxi & delivery
apps.description:
The best way to appreciate the convenience of our app is to download it and start using it to order a taxi and other transport. Rates vary. Ride to the railway station, airport, or another city. Pay by cash or card. Enjoy discounts and promo codes.
Since 2003, we’ve been developing innovative taxi ordering technologies, making our service more modern, affordable, and safe. Our service is helping millions of people save money as they commute and travel.

Price
If you need a cheap taxi every day, choose our Economy rate. If you value comfort, opt for the Comfort rate. We also have minivans, buses, and trucks. You can order a delivery of food, household cleaning products and other goods or medicine from shops and drugstores.
You can see your ride price before tapping the Order button, which is useful for planning your budget. Don’t worry about traffic – you only pay extra for additional services that were not specified in the order.
Enjoy the convenience of paying for rides with cash and a credit card. You can use a personal account that you refill whenever necessary for corporate or family rides.
It’s easy to get discounted rides if you use a promo code or you are one of our regular clients.

Order
You can order a ride by filling in the From and To address fields or using a city map. You can also use your smartphone’s or tablet’s location services.
A scheduled order helps you plan your rides for a convenient time.
You can provide special requests for your ride to arrange any necessary additional services: specify information about children, pets, or luggage; or add another phone number to order a taxi for someone else from your phone.
A driver can buy goods, medicine or groceries, and deliver them to your place.
Launch our app on Wear OS smart watch to track your ride status.
View a map to see available cars and your driver’s movement as he or she approaches your location.
You can share your location while you are en route. This is an important feature for parents who want to know their children are safe.
Leaving a ride rating affects the driver’s rating and helps us improve our service.

Countries
Argentina, Azerbaijan, Bangladesh, Brazil, Cambodia, Colombia, Dominican Republic, Indonesia, Kazakhstan, Kyrgyzstan, Laos, Malaysia, Peru, Philippines, South Africa, Tajikistan, Tanzania, Thailand, Uzbekistan, Vanuatu, Vietnam

apps.title: Lalamove - Fast & Affordable
apps.description:
Lalamove – 24/7 On-Demand Delivery App
Need something delivered fast?  Lalamove instantly connects you with a vast network of driver partners for fast, simple, and affordable deliveries anytime, anywhere. Founded in Hong Kong in 2013, we now serve 14 markets across Asia, Latin America, and EMEA, empowering businesses and individuals with hassle-free logistics. 

Fast and 24/7 Delivery Service
Get matched with a driver fast, any time of day or night. From urgent deliveries to scheduled business shipments, we're here 24/7 with on-demand, same-day, next-day, and scheduled options. Need multiple stops? We're here for your delivery needs. For added convenience, we also offer add-on services such as helper assistance and the ability to arrange multiple stops for your delivery needs.

Wide Range of Vehicle Options for Every Need
From small parcels to large loads, we have the right vehicle for your delivery:
- Trucks: For furniture moves and bulk shipments
- Vans: For business logistics and mid-size loads
- Motorcycles: For quick, small-item deliveries

Efficient and Affordable Services 
Get affordable delivery services with Lalamove's budget-friendly rates. Know your exact fee before booking – no hidden charges, no surprises. Our competitive pricing system helps you plan deliveries and trips while keeping costs low. Pay directly through the app or make a cash payment to your driver.

Professional and Reliable Drivers
Make your deliveries with our experienced and trained drivers. Lalamove ensures your packages are always secure.

Real-Time Tracking
Track your shipment's location and estimated arrival time in real-time through the app from the moment it departs. Facilitate your planning by controlling the delivery process.

Earn Rewards While You Deliver
Every delivery earns you LalaPoints, which can be redeemed for exclusive rewards and discounts, making each transaction more rewarding.

Delivery for Anything, Big or Small
From urgent documents and small parcels to large furniture and construction materials, we handle it all:
- Small packages and urgent documents
- Furniture, second-hand items, and office relocations
- Wholesale products and commercial transportation
- Construction materials and large loads
- Grocery items, food, flowers, and gifts
- And much more!

NEW: Rides for Every Need & Budget in Indonesia, Malaysia, Philippines,  Thailand, Vietnam! 
Lalamove is now offering ride-hailing services, providing an affordable and pleasant transportation experience. Whether you need a ride for your daily commute to school or work, or a convenient transfer to the airport, Lalamove offers the flexibility to book instantly or schedule in advance at affordable rates. Enjoy the added assurance of real-time tracking, allowing you to monitor your ride and travel with peace of mind.

Download our app and easily access special experiences, promotions and discounts so you can enjoy your favorite McDonald's products for much less than what you usually pay.  

You will receive alerts at the moment to find out in scoop of our new coupons and offers available to you.

  In addition, to help you choose your favorite product, we show you all the products with their nutritional information of your favorite hamburger or sandwich, desserts, beverages, salads and cravings.

apps.title: Chowdeck | Food Delivery
apps.description:
At Chowdeck, we deliver happiness straight to you, one delicious meal at a time.

Africa’s leading on-demand online food delivery service, Chowdeck, offers quick and convenient food delivery from hundreds of your favourite restaurants! Browse our extensive food menu, order food online, and enjoy fast and reliable delivery right to your door. Say goodbye to long queues and waiting time with Chowdeck!

Enjoy a variety of cuisines, including:

- African & Fast Food (Jollof rice, Pasta, Burgers, Waakye, Kelewele)
- Asian (Chinese, Indian, Japanese, and Lebanese)
- Drinks (Alcoholic and Non-Alcoholic)
- Mexican (Tacos)
- Halal friendly
- Healthy / Vegetarian (Breakfast, Smoothies, Fresh Fruit Juices)
- Pastries (Cakes, Cookies, Meat pies, Sausage rolls) and more.

Eat your favourite meals where you like! Chowdeck delivers food in numerous cities in Accra, Lagos and Abuja, including Yaba, Alausa, Ikoyi, Ogudu, Wuse, Gwarinpa, Lekki, Victoria Island, Ikeja, Surulere, Festac, Amuwo Odofin, Egbeda, Alimosho, Gbagada, Ikoyi, Jahi, Maitama, Garki, Jabi, Utako, Mabushi, Katampe, Kado Wuye, Apo, Gudu, Life Camp, 1st Avenue, Asokoro, Jahi, Wuse and Central Areas with ongoing expansions to other major cities across the continent.

With Chowdeck, order food online and get it delivered to you immediately or at a scheduled time. Alternatively, order ahead online and pick it up at your favourite restaurants.

Get notified from when the restaurant accepts your meal to when it arrives. Track your meal every second of the way between the restaurant and delivery.

Our restaurant partners include Honeysuckle, Papa's Pizza, Mega Chicken, Ajishafe, Burger King, Mama JB Takeout Restaurant, Jay’s Diner, King Glab, Korede Spaghetti, Panarotti’s Pizza, Fruits2Go, Amoke Oge, Saminu Kilishi, KFC, Debonair’s Pizza, Mr Biggs, Yakoyo, Labule, Red Gourmet Kitchen, El Padrino’s, Iyan Aladuke, The Place, Cubana Fish, DO Bowls, Food Fusion, Johnny Rocket, Papiees Maestro, Keje Grill, Ojuelegba Restaurant, So Fresh, Eden Life, Korean Wife’s Table, Squizz’d, Cookie Nation, Old English, and more.

Shop your groceries online easily from leading supermarkets, including Blenco, FoodCo and Domino Supermarket. Buy household needs, including beauty and cosmetics, self-care, baby food, pet needs, snacks, drinks, cleaning supplies and grocery staples such as bread, milk, chocolates, coffee, sugar, fruits, vegetables, frozen foods, and alcoholic beverages.

The Chowdeck Lifestyle is marked by ease and enjoyment. We offer our beloved customers unique perks like discounts, free delivery, and promotions through our in-app loyalty program and partnerships with local and international companies.

What are you waiting for? Order food online with Chowdeck and enjoy fast, convenient delivery wherever you are!

- Enter your location and find restaurants and supermarkets delivering to your location.
- Browse meals and products listed from restaurants and supermarkets near you.
- Pay online, sit back, and relax.
- Track your order in real-time in-app and through notifications.
- Rate and review your experience.

Any questions? Contact our Support team at https://chowdeck.com/contact

- Instagram - https://instagram.com/chowdeck

apps.title: Shgardi | شقردي
apps.description:
Are you thinking about dinner for tonight, grocery for home, Or an early morning coffee ? Then Shgardi app is your magical solution.
You can order anything through Shgardi app, by selecting the wanted store either through typing the store name in the search bar, selecting it from the nearby stores, or by defining its exact location in the map.  After submitting the order requests, one of our couriers will go directly to the shop to pick up the requested order. While he is in his way to deliver your order, you can find his location in the map and track his movements all the way from the store to your delivery location. You can choose your delivery location based on your personal preference, whether its home, office, or any other location. You can too save your favorite delivery locations for convenience purpose. 
 
We are distinguished at Shgardi by the sufficient quantity of couriers in every area we serve, and this resulted in a very quick delivery service for our customers, at any given time.
Our delivery price is the best among the market, and this is basically due to the elimination of commissions fees imposed on the couriers by other delivery apps. The full amount of delivery costs goes directly to the couriers, which entitle us to set competitive delivery price, without facing objection from our couriers.
If you have any issue regarding your request, you can reach our support center at any time during week 24/7. You can communicate with our support center either through an instant chat in the app with one of our agents, or by calling the united call center number.
You can order from Shgardi whatever you want from restaurants, grocery, perfumes, juices, sweets, or any place in the map, at the best price and top-quality service. Simply, Shgardi is your strategic partner for delivery needs.
Shgardi is currently working in kingdom of Saudi Arabia.

apps.title: Parcel - Delivery Tracking
apps.description:
If you are looking for an app to track deliveries on iPhone, iPad, Mac or Apple Watch - Parcel is the best choice for you. 

With this application you can promptly access tracking information for 300 delivery services, including UPS, USPS, FedEx, DHL, TNT, LaserShip, Aramex, OnTrac, China Post, Amazon Logistics and many other carriers. Full list of supported carriers is available at: https://parcel.app

With our unique carrier recognition function, adding a new delivery is just a matter of seconds. Sometimes you won't even need to enter a tracking number, you can use a barcode scanner which is available right in the app. 

Amazon integration in Parcel allows you to get your packages added automatically from your Amazon account. Once an order is shipped, it will appear in Parcel. This is done in a secure and privacy-friendly way with your credentials never leaving the device.

You can also locate your delivery on the map or manage your deliveries using Web Access (web.parcelapp.net) - easy and simple. Parcel has a native macOS app available for free in the Mac App Store.

Parcel utilizes the power of iOS to provide you the best possible user experience. You can use its widgets to see your upcoming deliveries and the share extension to add a new delivery directly from any other app.

Push notifications provided by Parcel are more convenient than from any other app. They are being sent only from 8am to 10 pm according to your timezone, so you will not be bothered at night (however, you can disable this option in the settings).

Some features, such as push notifications and tracking more than 3 deliveries are limited to premium subscribers. Current price for the premium subscription is $4.99 per year, and may vary from country to country. Parcel's privacy policy, as well as subscription terms are available at https://parcel.app/privacy-with-terms.html.

raw_data.releaseNotes:
Improved Sharing Experience
When you receive a shared delivery via a Parcel link, you no longer need to manually add it. You can now preview and view its details instantly — particularly useful for Amazon deliveries due to account restrictions.

Previews in Spotlight
Spotlight search has been enhanced. You can now use the Quick Look extension to preview delivery information directly within Spotlight.

Changes to Widgets
Parcel widgets now use App Intents for configuration. You may need to readjust your widget settings and/or restart your device to complete the migration.

Improved Device Management
When managing linked devices in the app settings you can now revoke multiple devices at once.

New API for Adding Deliveries
We’ve introduced a new API that allows you to add deliveries directly to your account. Documentation is available at web.parcelapp.net.

apps.title: getir: groceries, food&beyond
apps.description:
Experience unparalleled convenience with Getir. Getir delivers your daily essentials - fresh ingredients, delightful restaurant meals, and even that last-minute birthday card - directly to your doorstep in minutes. Plus, say goodbye to waiting in line for a taxi. With thousands of services available at your fingertips, Getir frees up your time and takes care of the errands, making life simpler.

Discover thousands of products instantly with Getir, spanning categories like Snacks, Water & Beverages, Ice Cream, Baked Goods, Home Care, Personal Care, and Pet Products. Getir, Turkey's premier delivery app, caters to your immediate needs. Say goodbye to trips to the store; let the store come to you!

Experience effortless shopping with GetirMore! Browse thousands of products from diverse categories without the need to step foot in a store. Our couriers will deliver everything right to your door! From electronics to automotive supplies, sports gear, and beyond, enjoy a wide selection of products backed by n11 quality. Say goodbye to grocery runs, simply place your order and let GetirMore take care of the rest! 

Getir not only covers your grocery needs but also satisfies your cravings with delicious meals delivered to your doors with GetirFood! Enjoy swift delivery from nearby restaurants whenever you're hungry. We're here to bring quality meals from top restaurants, just a tap away! With both cash and online payment options available, satisfying your cravings has never been easier!

Explore a universe of local shopping with GetirLocals! From your neighborhood butcher, greengrocer, bakery, pet shop, electronics store, to herbalist, we've got you covered. Additionally, with GetirWater, you can have freshness delivered to your door with just a tap. Our aim is to simplify your daily life with fast and local support.

Getir goes beyond groceries and food; it's your solution for transportation too! With Bitaxi, hail a taxi to anywhere you want, and with GetirDrive, easily rent nearby vehicles for smooth rides. And when your journey ends, just find a convenient spot to park!

Get your groceries, food, and water delivered in minutes with Getir! Experience ultimate convenience with our fast, reliable, and seamless delivery service. Order with just a tap, and enjoy big savings with our wide variety of promotions on food and grocery orders. Plus, benefit from 24/7 live support for any questions or concerns.

Lightning-fast delivery
Mouthwatering food
Effortless online ordering
Thousands of products
Taxi and vehicle support
Outstanding deals
Fresh and high-quality products
Flexible payment options
User-friendly interface

apps.title: inDrive. Save on city rides
apps.description:
inDrive, formerly known as inDriver, is a revolutionary ride-share application that boasts a presence in over 888 cities across 48 countries. Best of all, it’s completely free to use!

We're a new kind of rideshare app. We started up from scratch in 2013, and since then we've grown like crazy all around the world.
And now we're bringing our game-changing rides to the USA!

It’s an excellent taxi alternative for your trip. You can either find a ride or offer your own driving services through the app, making it super convenient and flexible. inDrive is a great ride-sharing option for rides in Miami. 

MORE CONTROL
Set the price you're happy to pay for rides and choose the driver you want to take you

FAIR PRICES
Our rides are cheaper because we don't charge drivers big fees

SAFETY FIRST
Vetted drivers, in-app safety features and a dedicated 24/7 support team

As a driver, you have the potential to earn more than a traditional cab driver using a standard transportation app. This is because you have the flexibility to create your own transport schedule and select which rides you wish to take.

Why Choose inDrive (a ride app or a driving app)

LOW SERVICE PAYMENTS FOR DRIVERS

We keep our service payments as low as we can, and they'll actually be 0% for six months from our launch.
We think it’s fairer this way. To us, you’re not just another driver who should simply take the rides we give you at the price we decide — no way, you're one of the team. 

QUICK AND EASY

Requesting an affordable ride is quick and easy with this ride-share app. Simply enter your starting point (A) and your destination (B), set your desired fare and select a driver to get started.

OFFER YOUR PRICE

We understand that finding a reliable and affordable ride can be a stressful experience. That’s why we want to offer you an alternative to traditional cab booking apps. With inDrive, you have the power to customize your rideshare experience. You can choose the driver you feel most comfortable with and set the price that works best for you. 

CHOOSE YOUR DRIVER

With inDrive, you have the power to select your driver from a list of those who have accepted your ride request. In addition, unlike other taxi booking apps, we offer you the freedom to choose based on factors such as price, car model, arrival time, rating, and the number of trips completed. This unique feature sets us apart as a preferred alternative to traditional cab apps.

STAY SAFE

Before accepting a ride, you can view the driver’s name, car model, license plate number, and the number of completed trips. This level of transparency is not standard in traditional taxi apps. Additionally, our app includes a “Share Your Ride” button, allowing you to share your trip details with family or friends. Our team is dedicated to developing new safety features to ensure a completely secure experience for both riders and drivers.

ADD EXTRA OPTIONS

By using this alternative taxi application, you have the option to include any specific requirements or additional information in the comments section, such as “traveling with my pet” or “carrying luggage.” The driver will be able to view this information on their driving app before deciding to accept your request.

JOIN AS A DRIVER & MAKE EXTRA MONEY

If you own a car, you can make extra money with our driving app. Unlike other cab booking apps, inDrive lets you view the passenger’s destination and price before accepting the ride. If the price seems inadequate, inDrive offers the option to suggest an alternative price or decline the ride request without penalties. Moreover, this car booking app has low-to-no service rates, meaning you can make more money while driving with this taxi app alternative.

Whether you are looking for a new driver app for your trip or need a ride in Miami, you can get a unique rideshare experience with this great cabs & taxi alternative. Install inDrive (inDriver) to ride & drive on your terms!

Craving a delightful coffee, a hearty brunch, or a sumptuous dinner? With Careem DineOut, you can enjoy up to 50% off at a curated selection of top cafes and restaurants across Riyadh. Whether you're seeking a cozy café ambiance or a vibrant dining experience, Careem DineOut connects you to the best spots in the city. No vouchers, no hassle—just effortless dining and great discounts. Savor delicious meals today!

Get your groceries delivered in just 20 minutes with Careem Market by Tamimi! Enjoy the trusted quality of Tamimi Markets, now with the convenience and speed of Careem. Get your groceries delivered in 20 minutes — no stress, no hassle.
From fresh milk, eggs, and bread to your favorite snacks, Careem brings you everything you need, exactly when you need it. Enjoy quality you trust at prices you'll love.

* Daily staples: milk, bread, butter, eggs, cheese
* Your favorite snacks, biscuits, chips, ice cream & chocolates

* Personal care essentials, cleaning & laundry supplies

Reliable and Timely Service
Experience our supercharged delivery network, ensuring your orders arrive exactly when you expect them - no delays, no hassle.


Download Careem Today
Take back your time and enjoy the convenience of having everything you need in one app. Because with Careem, you've got better things to do.

SUPPORT YOUR NEIGHBORHOOD

ORDER TAKEOUT OR DELIVERY

SIMPLE ORDERING & LOWER PRICES

apps.title: EatStreet Local Food Delivery
apps.description:
Take the quickest shortcut from hungry to happy with the EatStreet iOS app for food delivery & takeout.

Life’s easy with EatStreet - breakfast, brunch, lunch, dinner, or snacks - you don’t have to worry about it. The EatStreet food delivery app is your craving quencher for meals, drinks, snacks, appetizers and shareable food for parties: Available in over 250 cities throughout the U.S.! We offer fast pickup and food delivery from local restaurants and diners.
 
Our fast-growing EatStreet restaurant delivery app offers cheap food delivery in major cities including: 
-Illinois - DeKalb; 
-Iowa - Ames, Dubuque, Waterloo/Cedar Falls; 
-Kansas - Lawrence, Manhattan, Salina, Topeka; 
-Wisconsin - Appleton, Eau Claire, Fond du Lac WI, Green Bay, Janesville, Kenosha, La Crosse, Madison, Manitowoc, Milwaukee, Oshkosh, Sheboygan, Stevens Point, Wausau.

EatStreet partners with many local and chain restaurants in your city, neighborhood, or college town to provide diverse food choices: pizza, pasta, burgers, wings, tacos, etc. Some of our favorite food spots include Applebee's, Taco Johns, Toppers Pizza, Potbelly, Qdoba, Noodles & Company, Dairy Queen, Kwik Trip/Kwik Star and many more.

Order from home or work - just for yourself, or surprise everyone with a delicious treat! Need a celebratory cake or donuts at work? We’ve got you covered!

Dig into our hunger-solving Apple App features:

1. EatStreet Exclusive Coupons:
When you order food with the EatStreet App, we'll hook you up with exclusive coupons, restaurant specials, and rewards. We partner with many popular local restaurants from mom-&-pop diners to the big brands that everyone knows and loves. So the more you order to eat, the more you earn!  

2. Explore Different Cuisines: 
Order Chinese food; Get pizza delivered; Find your favorite sushi and pad thai; No matter what kind of food you crave, we've got you covered - Italian, Chinese, Mexican, Mediterranean, keto, vegetarian, vegan, pescatarian, gluten free and more!
 
3. Food Photography & Restaurant Reviews: 
Check out local favorite dishes and menu items before you order! You can even check-out photos of some of the tasty eats & read restaurant reviews to take the guessing out of what you're getting. 
 
4. Track Food Orders: 
There's no worse feeling after ordering food than not knowing where your order is. With our new EatStreet Food Order Tracker, you can check the status of your grub from the second you place your order until it's at your front door.  

5. Convenient Payment Options:  
The EatStreet iOS App offers a variety of ways to pay. You can always use credit card or PayPal, as well as using secure Apple Pay! Our EatStreet food ordering app allows you to pay for your meal as a group or an individual: great for work, parties and get-togethers.
 
6. Multiple Ways to Order Food:
Order Again: Having food deja? Our ‘Order Again’ feature makes it incredibly easy to reorder your favorite dishes.
Group Ordering & Split the Bill: Invite friends and start a group order. We’ll even split the bill so you don't get stuck ponying up for the "I'll pay you back later" people.
Order Ahead: Need food in the future? Place a delivery pickup order in advance. Your food will be piping hot and ready, right when and where you want it to be.
 
Ready to order with EatStreet? Here’s how to get started with your first food delivery:

  1. Download EatStreet iOS delivery app today!
  2. Create your account and login
  3. Pick from your favorite food spots
  4. Choose your meal and delivery type
  5. Pay and place your food order
  6. Track your delivery progress
  7. Enjoy your delicious food.

EatStreet is the perfect food ordering app for all your favorite grub & local eats. Order the meal you crave from local restaurants you love. Download the EatStreet food delivery app now!

Hungry. Happy. EatStreet.

raw_data.releaseNotes: Thanks for choosing EatStreet as your shortcut from hungry to happy! We update our app to improve your experience with faster and more reliable performance. This update introduces the EatStreet Cashback program and makes updates to our payment processor. Download the latest update today to check out the newest restaurants, app features, exclusive offers & more!

apps.title: Papa Johns Pizza & Delivery
apps.description:
The Papa Johns Pizza App makes ordering your favorite pizza online even easier! You can earn free food, find Papa Johns restaurant locations near you, get special online pizza offers, and track your pizza delivery order right to your door.

Place your order at any Papa Johns Pizza with no contact pizza delivery and safe store pickup options! For the convenience of our customers, all delivery orders will now use our safe and simple No Contact Delivery by default.

Earn Free Food & Pizza
Earn Papa Rewards points and redeem your Papa Dough towards free food or pizza items!

Special Food Delivery Offers
Get great offers & deals on delivery from your neighborhood Papa Johns Restaurant. Craving a tasty slice of pizza? Turn on push notifications to make sure you never miss an online offer for your next mobile food order and pizza delivery. 
 
Favorites and Past Pizza Orders 
Save time on your next food delivery with your Pizza faves and past orders. Quickly reorder from your favorites, or from any pizza order in the past 90 days, with an account. 

Find Your Local Papa Johns Pizza Restaurant
Easily search by zip code or city to find your local Papa John's Pizza restaurant for effortless online orders, speedy delivery or takeout. Take advantage of special local deals and discounts on your favorite pizzas!


Pay For Your Pizza Your Way
Our app makes it easy to pay for your pizza delivery or carryout order how you want by choosing from cash, credit card or Google Pay. 

Order Pizza & Food Ahead
Use our convenient Future Ordering for your next Papa Johns Pizza restaurant order! The Papa Johns app makes it easy to order tomorrow’s lunch or this weekend's party spread in advance. Choose when you'd like your food to be delivered or ready for pick-up.

Papa Track Your Pizza
Easily track your food or pizza delivery order from dough to door so you know when your food will arrive! Activate push notifications so you know when your order is on its way and get ready for pizza!

The Papa Johns Pizza app is for Papa Johns Restaurants in the United States.

If you have any questions or comments, please contact us at http://www.papajohns.com/contact-us/

Get up to ₹100 off on your first Zepto order, as a gift from us. 

So, what all can Zepto deliver in 10 minutes? Glad you asked. 

Short answer: Everything. 
Long answer 

Groceries for dinner. And a cooker to make your special biryani. 

We deliver both in 10 minutes 

Need headphones for a meeting. And a coffee to focus. 

We deliver both in 10 minutes 


Dumbbels for the gains and ice packs for the strains 

We deliver both in 10 minutes

From chart paper & school bags to the latest toys for your kids. 
From breakfast essentials & dry fruits to fresh meat for meals that fill you with nutrition. 
From sanitary pads to sexual wellness products & haircare to skincare for taking good care of yourself. 

You get the drift. Over 2,00,000 products from top brands at the lowest prices all over India. Delivered to your doorstep in just 10 minutes. 

Talking about lowest prices: Meet Super Saver 

Your license to shop for groceries at the lowest possible prices 

Get the lowest prices in the entire country and get your groceries delivered in 10 minutes. Stock up on your weekly essentials with the best possible prices. 

You can look around but you won’t find prices lower than Zepto Super Saver. It’s a challenge. 

Want some tea? Say hello to Zepto Café 

Ever felt like having a snack but cooking feels like too much effort? Need a coffee in the office but you have another call scheduled for 10 minutes? Unannounced guests coming over?

For all these situations (and many more) – You can now worry less and trust Zepto Café to deliver fresh food in just 10 minutes. 

From coco to momo, from upma to pakora, from idli to bhelpuri, from pavs to baos, from dal makhani to Hyderabadi biryani, from margherita to shahi tukda, and from cakes to shakes 

Café delivers over 2000 dishes and drinks to your doorstep in just 10 minutes 

All the speed, 0 compromises 

Everything that reaches your doorstep – from fresh fruits, leafy vegetables to dairy, bread and groceries – goes through multiple quality checks. Only those products that pass these checks are delivered to you! 


Where can you use Zepto 

Agra, Ahmedabad, Alwar, Ambala, Amritsar, Anand, Bareilly, Belgavi, Bengaluru, Bhiwadi, Chandigarh, Chatrapati Sambhaji Nagar, Chennai, Coimbatore, Dehradun, Delhi, Devangere, Faridabad, Ghaziabad, Gorakhpur, Gurugram, Haridwar, Hisar, Hubballi, Hyderabad, Indore, Jaipur, Jalandhar, Kanpur, Kochi, Kolkata, Kota, Kurukshetra, Lucknow, Ludhiana, Madurai, Meerut, Mehsana, Mumbai, Mysuru, Nagpur, Nashik, Neemrana, Noida, Palakkad, Panchkula, Panipat, Prayagraj, Pune, Rajkot, Roorkee, Saharanpur, SAS Nagar, Sonipat, Surat, Thrissur, Tiruchirappalli, Tumkuru, Udaipur, Vadodara, Valsad, Varanasi, Vellore, Vijayawada, and Warangal.

If we aren’t delivering in your area yet, don’t worry. We are adding new locations every day and will start delivering in your area super soon. 

What’s coming next? Everything 

From just groceries to getting a new phone in your hands in just 10 minutes – we’ve come a long way! 

Every day, we are adding new categories of products in cities across India so Indians can spend less time worrying about things and more time doing things they love.


We are excited for you to join the 30 cr+ users who have installed the app and are enjoying the magic of Zepto’s 10 minute delivery

apps.title: Slice: Pizza Delivery/Pick Up
apps.description:
Order from your favorite pizzeria with Slice. We empower your go-to local independent pizza shop so you can get the food you love fast, easy, and with tracked delivery. 

There’s no crazy fees for you or your pizzeria, and you’ll earn free pizza for being a loyal customer!

Put Local Shops First
Local pizzerias are at the heart of our communities. And we’re here to keep it that way. Slice gives your favorite independent pizza shop the tools and tech they need to thrive. That means they have more time to focus on making tasty pizza, and you get your order fast, tracked, and accurate. 

Get Real Pizza
Our independent pizzeria partners serve up deliciously authentic local pizza in communities all across the country. Slice works behind the scenes with your local shop so you can easily customize your pizza exactly how you like it. Extra cheese? You got it. Half pepperoni, half pineapple? No problem. Get your pizza, your way. With the Slice app, you can also save your go-to order for next time.

Earn Free Pizza
Yep, really. You’ll earn one Pizza Point for every order over $15, and it only takes eight Pizza Points to earn a free large cheese pizza. And speaking of free, your first Pizza Point is on us.

Better Food, Better Service
Why settle for fast food delivery when you can get delicious pizza from local shops delivered by a trusted pizza person straight to your door? Slice has the answer to those three magic words: “Pizza near me”. Or mozzarella sticks, wings, hot wings, salads, pasta… Do your food ordering, then opt for pizza delivery, take out, pickup, takeaway, contactless curbside pickup, or no-contact delivery. You can use our pizza tracker for live updates at every step, and whether you prefer credit card, PayPal, Google Pay, or Apple Pay, every type of payment is secure. Pizza is almost always perfect, but just in case, our top-ranked customer support team works hand-in-hand with your local shop to get you exactly what you want. 

Save Time, Save Money
The Slice app isn’t just the easiest way to order pizza — it also shows you your favorite pizzeria’s latest special offers, exclusive deals, and promotions. There’s no inflated prices or hidden charges because unlike third-party delivery apps, Slice is your shop’s direct partner. Switch from ordering on those delivery apps to ordering directly with Slice and you could save big: The average family saves over $200 a year! Slice makes it easy to get the food you love for less money, all while supporting your community’s restaurants. 

One-Tap Ordering, Real-Time Tracking
Slice the pizza app makes ordering easy (and reordering even easier). You’ll get an estimated delivery time for your pizza. Plus, keep your eyes on the pies with Slice’s real-time pizza tracker.

Find Your Favorite Restaurants on Slice
As well as neighborhood spots, we’re proud to partner with local favorites like Jet's Pizza, Cicis Pizza, Round Table Pizza, Uno Pizzeria & Grill, Rosati's Pizza, Patxi's Pizza, Vocelli Pizza, and Sarpino’s Pizzeria, plus over 20,000 more local restaurants in hundreds of locations across the country for takeout or delivery.

Get the pizza app that connects you to your favorite local pizzerias. You’ll enjoy the freshest, most authentic pizza in your neighborhood, without any phone calls, “hold pleases,” or busy signals when you try to figure out where your food is! 

Download the Slice app today, order tasty food, and make tonight your best pizza night yet.

These behind-the-scenes improvements make it easier for you to support your neighborhood pizzeria (and enjoy delicious pizza).

Download the Slice app today, order tasty food, and make tonight your best pizza night yet.

Snappy Shopper: delivering food, drink and household goods from your local store to door from as little as 30 minutes – and completely contact free!

Forgotten the milk? 
Running out of time to get to the shops? 
Need a home delivery slot TODAY? 

You need Snappy Shopper. Tap in your postcode and order groceries from your local store, then let Snappy Shopper deliver directly to your door from as little as 30 minutes. 
Delivering from top convenience stores including Nisa, SPAR, Premier, One Stop, Costcutter, EVF and co-op food, Snappy Shopper can satisfy your same day home delivery needs. 

With hundreds of local Snappy Shopper stores, we have quickly become the UK's fastest growing grocery delivery service! Snappy Shopper retailers offer a wide range of products, from milk and bread to confectionary and household items to satisfy your online grocery shopping needs.

apps.title: Sunbasket Meal Delivery
apps.description:
YOUR PERSONAL CHEF IN A BOX
Here comes the Sunbasket, your go-to source for fresh prepared meals and mouthwatering recipes featuring organic fresh produce. We partner with the country’s top farmers, producers, and fishermen to bring the best ingredients under the sun: responsibly-sourced meats, sustainable seafood, and peak-season flavors. 

Discover nutritious and delicious recipes crafted by our team of award-winning chefs. From breakfast to dinner to everything in between, we pick, prep, and perfect our meals—so you can take it easy.

DINNER IN MINUTES 

Short on time? Just heat up our Fresh & Ready dinners for a no-fuss meal in as little as 6 minutes. Light on effort and rich in flavor, these fresh (never frozen!) dinners make healthy eating easy peasy.

FRESH WEEKLY RECIPES
We picked the best ingredients, now you pick the best meals. Choose your favorite meal plan or mix and match from over 24 weekly recipes. Either way, variety is always on the menu.

DELIVERED TO YOUR DOOR

Presto! Your go-to dinner is now your come-to dinner. With one simple tap (and a little happy dance), get all your favorite meals delivered to your doorstep.

EAT SOMETHING AWARD-WINNING 
Our team of award-winning chefs develop, test, and perfect each dish, so you get five-star deliciousness in every bite. It’s like having your own personal sous chef.

FLEXIBLE SUBSCRIPTION
Manage your subscription anytime, anywhere. Use our app to schedule weekly deliveries, customize your menu, and discover quick and easy recipes. Need to skip, cancel, or forward your box? Sure thing.

apps.title: Yandex Go: Taxi Food Market
apps.description:
Yandex Go
Rides, Market, scooters, package and food delivery

• RIDES
Pick your service class
Ride Economy for everyday errands. Comfort and Comfort+ to relax with more legroom. Minivan for big groups, traveling with skis or bicycles, or trips to the airport.

• SCOOTERS
Bright yellow Yandex Go scooters are already cruising cities. Rent up to three scooters from the same account, buy Minute Bundles to make rides more affordable, and use Yandex Plus to subscribe to Scooters for free unlocks.

• FOOD FROM RESTAURANTS
Order delivery from independent and popular chain restaurants. Stock up on snacks for a party, soup, khachapuri, wok, sushi, pizza, and vegan options.

• MARKET YANDEX GO
Market Yandex Go offers dozens of categories and millions of important, useful items in Russia and Uzbekistan. Enjoy the user-friendly search or select the categories to find what you're looking for. Add items to your cart, place and track your order — all in the Yandex Go app.
If you've already added items to your Yandex Market cart, you'll see your order in Yandex Go and can continue checkout there. If an item is out of stock, we'll suggest alternatives at about the same price.

• DELIVERY
Have a courier pick up your printer after repairs, hand over documents to a contractor, or haul off that old couch you sold. For large items, you can order a cargo truck. Couriers will arrive for pickup in just 15 minutes.

• TRANSPORT
View schedules for buses, trams, commuter trains, and other public transport, compare routes, and find the nearest stops and convenient transfers. Available in some cities for now.
 
Availability of services and options may vary depending on the region.

raw_data.releaseNotes: It's time to update the app! We fixed a few bugs and made some minor improvements to make it a bit faster, but you won't see any visual changes.

apps.title: Foxtrot Delivery Market
apps.description:
Say hello to your new corner store and delivery market. With the Foxtrot app, you have access to our entire curated collection of goods, all available for $3 delivery in as little as 30 minutes or for pickup in store. Find us in Chicago and Dallas!


~ Everyday Essentials, Local Faves, New Finds ~ 

From kelp chips to Cheez-its, we’ve got a little something for everyone. Whether it’s a midweek grocery delivery, lunch delivery or just stocking up for the party, you’re sure to discover your favorite snack or a local find you’ll love (hello, Jeni’s!). And with community at the heart of our business, we’re proud to stock our shelves with local brands from Chicago, Dallas, and D.C.


~ Wine & Beer Delivery ~

Drink delivery, anyone? Yep, with the Foxtrot app you can get wine, beer and alcohol delivered Use our app to browse our collection of wines, all handpicked by our very own sommelier. Organic, biodynamic, red, white, rose—whatever you’re looking for, we’ve got you covered. Discover your favorite craft beer and hard seltzers, and then place an order for delivery directly to your door or for pickup from one of our stores.


~ In-Store and Cafe Pickup ~

Order ahead and skip the line. With our app, you have access to In-Store and Cafe Pickup, allowing you to place your order ahead of time. If you’re browsing our entire collection, we’ll have your goods ready in under thirty minutes. If you’re ordering for coffee pickup, we’ll have your coffee ready in under ten—just the way you like it. Browse some fan favorites like avocado toast, breakfast tacos, draft cold brew, and so much more!


~ Pay in App & Perks ~

With our app, you can upload a payment method to your account and leave your wallet at home! And when you pay in app, you’re introduced to Perks, our rewards program that’s available exclusively through our app. With Perks, you can get things like free delivery, free coffee, happy hour pricing, and more. Just click the Perks tab in the app to learn more.

advisories: Infrequent/Mild Alcohol, Tobacco, or Drug Use or References

Get easy access to your ReadyRefresh® account and keep your favorite beverages stocked with a few taps on your phone. It’s convenient and straightforward to create and manage your deliveries, browse, and shop for products. You can even view invoices and make secure payments on the go.

New Features:
-      You can now purchase your dispenser using convenient 6 or 12-month installment plans
-      Schedule a professional cleaning service to ensure you are getting the most out of your dispenser

Key Features:
-      Manage your recurring products, make changes to future deliveries, keep track of delivery dates, and view past deliveries
-      See account balances, make payments, update payment methods, manage autopay, and opt-in or out of paperless billing
-      Unlock savings through personalized special offers
-      Easily upgrade to a Refresh+ membership for exclusive discounts
-      Change your address easily by visiting Account Details
-      Add a gate or property access code to your profile for seamless delivery
-      Improved and expanded Customer Support
-      Schedule empty bottle pickup
-      Create new one-time deliveries for a special event or occasion
-      On-Demand Customers can now build recurring orders
-      Manage multiple accounts
-      Refer-A-Friend

Enjoy healthy, homemade food cooked by our amazing and trusted home chefs. With only four steps between you and a home-cooked meal, it’s easier than you thought to order favorite authentic dishes.

apps.title: Shuttle: Food Delivery Korea
apps.description:
Food Delivery in Korea 


Order Food in Korea – Fast, Easy, and in English
Shuttle is Korea’s leading foreign-friendly food delivery app, trusted by expats, travelers, and the U.S. military community. Order food, groceries, and essentials from top local restaurants and shops—all in your language.


New users get ₩5,000 OFF their first order with code: SHUTTLE.


Key Features

· Local Eats, Delivered – Discover the best Korean and international restaurants near you.
· Seamless Pickups – Skip the line and collect your order with easy in-store pickup.
· Grocery Delivery – Get groceries, heat-to-eat meals, home essentials, and gifts with next-day delivery via Shuttle Market.
· English App & Support – No more language barriers! Order in English and get customer support via live chat.
· Multilingual App – Use the Shuttle app in your preferred language—now available in Korean (한국어), English, Vietnamese (Tiếng Việt), Thai (ภาษาไทย), Bahasa (Bahasa Indonesia), Japanese (日本語), Simplified Chinese (简体中文), Cantonese (粵語), French (Français), Spanish (Español), German (Deutsch), Arabic (العربية), Hindi (हिन्दी). *Please note: Menu content is currently available in English and Korean only. 
· Secure Payments – Pay with major international/Korean credit cards, PayPal, KakaoPay, or store your method for fast checkout.
· No Korean Phone Number Needed – Sign up with just an email, phone verification is optional (but required for using Shuttle credit).
· Shuttle e-Gifts – Send Shuttle credits to friends and family by email for birthdays, holidays, or just because.


Proudly Serving U.S. Military in Korea

Order easily near USAG Yongsan, Camp Humphreys, Osan Air Base, Kunsan Air Base, USAG Daegu, and more. Use your U.S. credit card  and enjoy trusted delivery from base-friendly restaurants.


Need Help?

Live chat is available in English or Korean. Or reach us at: info@shuttledelivery.co.kr

apps.title: ChowNow: Local Food Ordering
apps.description:
We’re not your usual ordering app. We don’t believe in crazy-high commissions for independent restaurants, to start. Or marked-up menu prices for you. But we still have delivery and takeout from the best local restaurants–so dig in.

EXPLORE NEARBY RESTAURANTS
Search for local takeout, delivery, or curbside pickup options by cuisine, restaurant name, deals and more. Maybe you’re looking for a specific type of food? Here’s a taste of what you could find on our app: Italian, Vietnamese, Korean, Japanese, Mexican, Thai, Greek, Chinese, French, Mediterranean, Indian, and a lot more. Check out our map to find places that are open right now, or offering a promotion. Order what you want by customizing menu items, and get it delivered with convenient, real-time tracking updates. 

CHECK OUT FAST
Enable Apple Pay or save your card info for easy payment and fast checkout. Plus, quick reordering options help you get your favorites again in a snap.

GET HELP FROM REAL HUMANS
We’re here 24/7. Reach out to our team via chat, SMS, phone, or email. We’re here around the clock if you need help—or just want to talk food.

WE’RE OPEN NEAR YOU
We’ll help you find the best restaurants at most U.S. locations. Order fresh flavors in Los Angeles, New York, Chicago, San Francisco, Washington DC, Boston, Atlanta, Denver, Portland, Seattle, Philadelphia, Brooklyn, Dallas, Austin, Orange County, San Diego, Cleveland, Minneapolis, and Charlotte.

STILL READING?
We like your style. How about pizza delivery, pasta, burritos, barbecue, sushi, salads, vegetarian, vegan, burgers and fries? 

We even have desserts, coffee, smoothies—you name it. So go for it. Download the app and grab something good. We’re here if you need help.

apps.title: Totally Reliable Delivery
apps.description:
Buckle up your back brace and fire up the delivery truck, it's time to deliver! Join up to three of your friends and haphazardly get the job done in an interactive sandbox world. Delivery attempted, that's a Totally Reliable Delivery Service guarantee!

FEATURES:
- Single Campaign and Online Multiplayer: Go it alone to ensure the safety of your deliveries, or join your friends and put your teamwork to the test.
- Controlled Noodly Chaos: Unpredictable ragdoll physics meets snappy platforming. Sprint, leap, dive, and grapple with ease, but collide with something and you'll be knocked out cold!

- Ragtag Crew: Customize your blue-collar workers and get your rear into gear, it's time to deliver!

You can also customize select recipes so you can make something fresh every single week. Home Chef makes delicious home cooking achievable.

- Curated for You: Discover tailored meal recommendations that match your preferences and cravings.

apps.title: Rose Delivery | Jordan
apps.description:
حمَّل تطبيق روز الآن و استمتع بتجربة خدمة توصيل الطلبات الجديدة ( تطبيق توصيل الطلبات الأفضل في الأردن  )
محتاج أي شي من أي مكان ولأي مكان وبأي وقت روز بيكفيك عناء الزحمة والمشوار، نزل طلبك وأحد مندوبينا رح يوصله لباب بيتك 
تطبيق روز مثالي لتوصيل الطلبات في كل من مدينة عمّان، الزرقاء، العقبة، إربد حيث يمكنكم طلب الطعام/طلبات المطاعم، نقل الأثاث، توصيل البضائع، توصيل الأغراض، إرسال واستلام الطرود، هدايا ،  و جميع خدمات التوصيل. فقط مع روز احصل على خدمة التوصيل الافضل في الأردن.
تطبيق روز يوفر تجربة جديدة لمفهوم توصيل الطلبات من خلال فريق مناديب منتشر بكافة أنحاء الأردن ، حيث يقوم العميل :
• بتحديد زمن توصيل الطلب ( الطلب الآن ، الطلب لاحقاً ) .
• تحديد مكان إستلام الطلب و من ثم مكان تسليم الطلب .
• ادخال تفاصيل الطلب و الإنتهاء بإرسال الطلب .
• و من ثم يتلقى العميل العديد من عروض الاسعار المرسلة من قبل فريق مناديب روز ، و يقوم العميل بإختيار العرض الأنسب .
يتيح تطبيق روز إمكانية التواصل مع المندوب الذي تم إختياره من قبل العميل من خلال صفحة محادثة مباشرة وفورية و إمكانية التواصل من خلال الإتصال الهاتفي المباشر ، كما يُلزم تطبيق روز المندوب بإرسال صورة عن الفاتورة ، وبتقدر تتبع طلبك من خلال خاصية التتبع و ,lومراقبة موقع المندوب أول بأول
مع تطبيق روز ما في داعي تطلع بالزحمة ، كل إللي عليك تفتح التطبيق و تطلب 
للمزيد من المعلومات، يمكنك التواصل معنا عبر
info@rosecity.app
www.rosecity.app



Rose Delivery App is a new service offered in Jordan for shoppers who don't want to go to market and they need someone else to buy their needs and deliver it to them.
From the comfort of your home, you can open the App and fill a request for purchasing your
needs from your selected shops and it will take no time until our drivers send you their quotations for the requested order, taking into consideration that you will provide in your
order an approximate price for what you want to buy, and a purchase bill will be provided by
the driver with your order.
After you receive many quotations for your order, you can select one of them and
communicate with the driver either by a phone call or through the messages in the App.
Usually it will take from 30 to 60 minutes until you receive your order to your doorstep.
Orders to purchase that can be placed in the system in limitless and can range from grocery to
food orders or anything else you might think of.
There's a wide range of vehicles available through the App, like 1 ton pickups, vans, passenger
cars  are available! so even if you are thinking of shifting your home or office
the App can help you with that!
bottom line: if you need a delivery of:
Food and meals
Grocery or shopping
Goods delivery
home shifting
furniture shifting
electrical household items delivery
Ikea furniture delivery and assembly
clothes from dry clean
clothes from tailor shop
shoes from repair shop
bread from the bakery
Mcdonald's meal
Burger king meal
Shawerma 3saj delivery
Burger maker meal delivery
or anything else you can think with!
Just download and install the application and you will enjoy the ease of the service that can be
provided to you.
Currently the App is focused on Amman City and other Jordanian Cities...in the future we will
expand to other countries as well!
For more information, you can communicate with us via
info@rosecity.app
www.rosecity.app

Hungry or Need Groceries in 10 minutes?

Welcome to Swiggy, your one-stop shop for online food ordering, groceries, dining, and convenient pickup & delivery!

Here's why India LOVES Swiggy:

• Order food & order groceries to get 10 min grocery delivery, & other essential services online
• Swiggy One users get unlimited Free Delivery on all orders including instant grocery
• Find top local restaurants like Mcdonald's & Burger King in your city
• Order Groceries like Maggi, Chocolate, and Amul fresh cream & enjoy lightening delivery in 10 Mins with Instamart
• Get discounts by paying dining out bills via our Dineout section
• Real-time updates on your food & instant grocery order status & an ETA 
• Make payments via VISA/MasterCard Credit or Debit Cards, Net Banking, Paytm, cash on delivery, credit services like LazyPay, & more

Food Delivery: Order Delicious Food With A Tap
Get Up To 60% Off + Free Delivery with Pocket Hero's picks

• No Minimum Order conditions, so you can order even a single item on Swiggy.
• Order chicken shawarma, Margherita pizza, masala dosa, burgers, pasta, coffee, chicken momos, desserts, & more.
• Explore our endless range of cuisines, including North Indian, Chinese food, South Indian, Thai, Healthy, Street Food, Breakfast, Late-Night Cravings, & more.
• Get North Indian food, Punjabi cuisine, South Indian cuisine, Italian and Bengali cuisine with top chains like Domino's Pizza, Wow Momo, KFC, Burger King, Pizza Hut, FreshMenu, McDonald's, Subway, Faasos, Starbucks coffee, and more.
• Find local restaurants, breakfast places, brunch spots, cafes & bars

INSTAMART - Get Anything In 10 Minutes

Instamart delivers groceries and more to your doorstep within 10 Minutes. Order groceries, emergency supplies, midnight cravings, cake deliveries, and more.

• From Knorr soup , fruit delivery, country delight ghee and diet coke, vegetables, Amul ice cream, Bisleri, dairy, Cadbury chocolate, cleaning essentials, personal care products like Santoor soap and Sunsilk shampoo, and baby care, you can find everything here.
• Present in 120+ cities, open from 6 a.m. to late at night* for 10 min grocery delivery like Maggi, Pringles Chips, Nescafe Coffee, and more.
*Opening & closing times might vary across cities owing to Govt. regulations.
• Grab 30,000+ products across groceries & other items like toys, stationery, home & kitchen appliances, electronics, beauty & more.

DINEOUT - deals on dining out at top restaurants

• Use Swiggy Dine out app to get up to 50% FLAT discounts with no upper limit on your dining-out bills.
• Over 40,000+ restaurants across 40+ cities 
• Up to 15% off on your bills with HDFC Bank Credit Cards
• Pre-book your table for hassle-free dining
• Find Cafes, bars, pubs, breweries, luxury dining, kid-friendly, rooftop dining, brunch buffets, and much more!

With Swiggy One, you'll experience savings like never before. 

• Order food online and get Unlimited free delivery + extra 30% discount from top restaurants
• Unlimited free delivery on all Instamart orders
• 0 surge fee

Order Food Delivery In Train IRCTC Delivery

Now, you can enjoy Swiggy's online food delivery even while traveling! With Swiggy's IRCTC delivery service, order food on train from top-rated restaurants at major railway stations and have it delivered directly to your train seat. Enter your train number, and let Swiggy handle the rest.

Publix Delivery lets you order groceries from your neighborhood Publix to be shopped and delivered by Instacart* the same day, in as little as one hour. 

 SHOP RIGHT FROM THE APP 
 Just create an Instacart account and then order from the South’s favorite supermarket via Instacart. Get fast deliveries to your door on groceries, home essentials, and more. You could also use the Publix Curbside service at select locations, and get your groceries shopped by skilled Publix associates right to your car.

apps.description:
חברת SOLO חושפת בפניכם עולם שלם שכולו כיף אחד גדול! ב SOLO המשלוחים המהירים ביותר מהמקומות השווים ביותר בלחיצת כפתור. 
ב סולו תוכלו למצוא מסעדות, פארם, סופר, פרחים, אטליז ועוד המון דברים שפשוט כיף להזמין במשלוח מהיר ומבלי לצאת מהבית.
אז שלא תגידו שלא אמרנו...זהירות - זה ממכר !
האפליקציה קלילה, כיפית, נוחה והכי חשוב מהירה.
איש חכם פעם אמר שלא פשוט להיות פשוט והוא אכן צדק ! SOLO משקיעה את מרבית מאמציה בחוויית המשתמש כדי שהאפליקציה תהיה ידידותית וקלה לתפעול כדי שגם סבא וסבתא יוכלו ליהנות מכל הטוב הזה.
פשוט נכנסים, בוחרים, ובתוך 30 דקות בממוצע יגיע שליח אדיב עד לפתח דלתכם.
בSOLO הכל ברור ושקוף, מיד בסיום ההזמנה תוכלו לראות היכן השליח נמצא ואת הזמן שנותר עד להגעתו.
למקרה שאתם לא בטוחים במשהו תמיד תוכלו לפנות אלינו דרך הצ׳אט בזמן שעות הפעילות ותוך מספר שניות נציג יעמוד לרשותכם.

אנו פועלים כרגע בחיפה, נשר, טירת הכרמל.
נשמח לקבל פידבקים ולדעת מה אתם חושבים.
פירגונים יתקבלו בברכה דרך שירות הלקוחות שלנו. 
אוהבים,
צוות - SOLO

apps.title: Mashkor: on-demand delivery
apps.description:
Hala wallah! Meet Mashkor, your delivery genie who's here to add a touch of enchantment to your day!

We help bring convenience to you! How?

By simply selecting BUY anything or PICK-UP anything!

BUY ANYTHING!

It's Friday night; you're invited to a wedding and have nothing to wear? We will get your dress delivered to your doorstep.

Last-minute gift shopping for a friend's birthday? Surprise them with a thoughtful present delivered on their special day.

Want to redecorate your living space without leaving home? We will get stylish decor, and furnishings delivered hassle-free.

PICK-UP ANYTHING!

Need to return an item to the store but can't find the time? We'll pick it up and handle the return for you.

Forgot your gym bag at home and can't make it to the gym? We'll pick it up and drop it off at your workout spot.

Need an urgent document from the office but are stuck at home? We'll pick it up and bring it to your doorstep.

Simple right? LOL

ps: if you're enjoying our app, please share your feedback by leaving a review.

Get ready for some serious magic!

Mashkor :)
