apps.title: 7-Eleven: Rewards & Shopping
apps.description:
Join. Earn. Get Rewarded.
 
SHOP & EARN REWARDS  
Get rewards points on your everyday purchases when you scan your app barcode*, then browse our rewards menu and use points to get free food and drinks. Earn faster with bonus points offers and point streaks on select snacks, drinks, and products. Don’t forget to take advantage of our punch cards to unlock additional free rewards!

FIND DEALS 
Get exclusive offers and money-saving deals on your favorite products like pizza, coffee, ice cream, donuts, snacks, energy drinks and bottled water for 7Rewards members. 

ORDER DELIVERY 
Get food, alcohol, candy, snacks, drinks, ice cream, coffee, groceries, health needs, household essentials, and more delivered anywhere you are in about 30 minutes. Super-Fast Delivery. Get your order delivered to your door 24/7. We deliver over 5000+ items including Slurpee® and Big Gulp®, coffee, pizza and sandwiches, and even beer, wine, and liquor (where available, 21 years or older of course) across major metro areas. 

FUEL SAVINGS & PRICE LOCK
Find our 7-Eleven branded gas stations and fill up on gas for less. On your first 7 trips, you'll save 11¢/gal. After that, you'll receive everyday member savings of at least 5¢/gal (varies by state). Plan your next gas station visit today with Price Lock. Price Lock secures the gas price for 4 days in a participating gas station by finding the lowest fuel prices around you and holds the price for you with Price Lock. Unlock and Re-Lock anytime and know you will always get the best price even if your locked price is higher.

7-ELEVEN WALLET 
It's easy to pay with your phone. The 7-Eleven Wallet makes checking out contactless and easy. Get started when you load your Wallet with cash, credit, debit, 7-Eleven gift cards or Apple Pay®.
   
MOBILE CHECKOUT - (AVAILABLE AT SELECT 7-ELEVEN LOCATIONS)  
With our contactless checkout, you can shop and check out with your phone. It’s as easy as scan, pay, and go. Scan the items as you shop and skip the line when you are ready to checkout. What’s more, Mobile checkout users get discounts, exclusive deals, special rewards, and rewards points on every transaction.

NOW AVAILABLE AT STRIPES STORES  
Start saving big and earning rewards points on everything you buy at Stripes stores. Redeem points for free food and drinks. Get tacos and family meals from Laredo Taco Company, beer, and groceries to go with curbside pickup at select stores.

*Points exclude services, fuel and age-restricted items including tobacco, lottery and alcohol

Whether you want to let your customer know their driver has arrived or let your dispatch operators know the status of the delivery, our app takes care of it all.

Quickly add items to your list or cart based on frequent purchases, recommendations and more. View and shop from past orders at any time.

Find hundreds of weekly coupons, deals and other offers. Plus, earn, track and redeem rewards as you shop.

apps.title: Phlenu Delivery
apps.description:
Introducing Phlenu Delivery - Unleashing the Power of Unrivaled, On-Demand Delivery Services.

Phlenu Delivery stands as your gateway to the epitome of swift, secure, and steadfast delivery services, all at the beck and call of your fingertips. We don't just deliver goods, we deliver promises, with an unprecedented zeal that makes us the speedier, more agile, and infinitely scalable option compared to traditional carriers or ad hoc couriers.

Phlenu Delivery: we bring you the freedom to effortlessly schedule pickups from your desired location, delivering to any corner of your town, city, or even across national boundaries.

Why Choose Phlenu Delivery?

Embrace Excellence
As the crown jewel of courier services in Ghana and Nigeria, Phlenu Delivery operates with an advanced dispatch and routing technology. We ensure your package is hand-delivered precisely where you need it, backed by a 100% guarantee for secure, punctual deliveries.

Unearth Affordable Convenience
At Phlenu Delivery, we serve more than just top-tier delivery services. We strive to provide unparalleled rates, continuously benchmarking the market to deliver the best value to our customers. We celebrate you with reduced rates, exceptional discounts, and exclusive deals.

Embark on an Earning Journey
Phlenu Delivery extends an attractive opportunity for licensed drivers and couriers to earn a rewarding income. Whether you're looking for part-time or full-time work, simply register online, start accepting orders, create a schedule that suits you, and commence earning by delivering smiles to our customers.

Experience Serenity
Bid farewell to the uncertainties of delivery schedules. With Phlenu Delivery, you can trace your deliveries in real-time, accessible on any device, anytime.

Here's How It Works

Post Your Delivery
From small tokens to sizable packages, Phlenu Delivery handles it all. Simply indicate your pick-up and drop-off points, and let us take the helm from there.

Obtain an Instant Estimate
Just share the destination of your package, and we'll provide you an instantaneous, transparent quote.

Enjoy Real-Time Tracking
Phlenu Delivery offers you the power of live tracking, eliminating the mystery of your package's whereabouts. Your peace of mind is just a click away.

Take charge of your deliveries with Veho!

We are a technology company rethinking last mile logistics. We enable personalized, fast, and transparent deliveries which means you can easily track and find up to date information about your orders.  

Realize you need to go into your office tomorrow? Veho provides the ability to quickly update your delivery information to ensure that your package gets to you.

With Veho you control the delivery down to the exact location you want the package delivered. Provide our delivery partners with instructions to leave the package at your front door, inside a storage locker, with a doorman, or next to the garden gnome.  

We're on a mission to reinvent the delivery experience:
- Easily track & find up to date information about your orders
- Quickly update your delivery information
- Add customizable delivery instructions
- Be able to quickly connect with our Support team over text

apps.title: DIG INN | Seasonal, fresh food
apps.description:
10 points for every $1 spent when you order DIG for delivery or pickup on the DIG app. With our new DIG Rewards program, every purchase unlocks reward progress and points toward the next loyalty tier. 

Use the DIG app to get your lunch or dinner delivered fast, for free. Order food online, or simply see where your nearest restaurant is located and what’s on the menu. Save your favorite items or reorder from your order history to quickly satisfy your vegetable needs. 

Getting DIG has never been easier. Schedule orders for takeout, and we’ll let you know when to pick it up. Or, we’ll deliver your food directly to you.

EARN REWARDS

Earn and redeem rewards both in-store and online through the app.

CUSTOMIZE YOUR ORDER

Craving a bowl? Prefer farro over rice? Feeling more greens over charred chicken? Build your own meal. We’ll take care of the rest.

FIND YOUR NEAREST DIG

If you’re looking for food in New York, Boston, Philadelphia, or a few other select locations, we can show you your closest restaurant.

BROWSE THE MENU

Our menu changes seasonally with what we can get our hands on — so make sure to check out the menu to see what we’re offering. Our menu also shows our many vegan food options, as well as allergy warnings.

TRACK YOUR PURCHASES

Really into what you ordered the last time, but can’t quite remember what it was? Take a look, and order it again.

EAT MORE VEGETABLES

They just taste good — especially when they’re delivered to your doorstep.

Questions or concerns? Find us on Facebook (facebook.com/diginnmarket), Twitter (@diginn), and Instagram (@diginn), or email (contact@diginn.com).

apps.title: Total Wine & More
apps.description:
Take Total Wine & More with you wherever you go! Our new app makes it easy to search our incredible product selections, shop and pickup in store, enjoy special offers and much more. Make your shopping simple and download our app today. 

EASY ORDERING 
Search our wide selection, find your local store and place orders quickly.  
  
SCAN & LEARN 
Use the barcode scanner to easily find product information, ratings and reviews.
  
DEALS 
Never miss out on a discount again! View the latest Limited-Time Specials and promotions on our deals page. 
  
IN-STORE PICKUP* 
Save time by selecting our express in-store pickup, which guarantees your orders will be ready in speedy fashion.  
  
ORDER TRACKING 
Never wonder where your order is with confirmation notifications and status updates.  
  
QUICK REORDERING 
Like what you’ve tried? You can easily reorder from your in-store and online purchase history.  
 
IN-STORE EVENTS 
Use our app to find and register for events and classes at your local store. 

DELIVERY
Don’t have enough time to stop in the store? We’ve got you covered! Just order on-the-go and select same-day delivery to get our wide selection delivered to your home or office at a time that’s convenient for you. Yes, deliver alcohol straight to your front door whether its wine, beer, spirits, tequila, vodka, and so much more!

CURBSIDE PICKUP*
We are launching contactless Curbside Pickup in select stores. Orders placed on the Total Wine app will be delivered to customers’ cars outside its stores by employees.

GROCERIES
We have snacks, food & beverages available for purchase in store.

COCKTAIL RECIPES 
Stir up some fun with our new recipes section on the homepage

GIFT CARD REDEMPTION 
Redeem your Total Wine and More Gift Card online! Enter in your gift card information for easy checkout

LIVE CHAT
Need help? Our customer service page now includes a live chat feature! Connect with our support team in real-time for instant assistance. 

*In-store pickup is available at all of our 250+ locations.
 
 
All aspects of the app (e.g., placing orders) can be used in states where we have stores (AZ, CA, CO, CT, DE, FL, GA, IL, KS, KY, MA, MD, MI, MN, MO, NC, NJ, NM, NV, NY, OK, SC, TN, TX, VA, WA, WI). To find a store near you, visit www.totalwine.com/store-finder.

If you would like to delete your account, please call us at (800) 949 - 9892

apps.title: efood delivery: food, grocery
apps.description:
efood - delivery in Greece

efood is the #1 online delivery platform in Greece and for good reason. It has so much to offer. We’ve brought together food, coffee, supermarkets, local neighborhood shops, offers, rewards, and so much more – all in one place! 

Whatever you want, whenever you want it, it’s just a few taps away!

• Coffee & food
You haven't cooked and you're hungry. We’ve been there. You woke up, and there's no way you’re getting up without a coffee. We get it. You always study late at night, but a chocolate-banana-cookie crepe could take your productivity to the next level. We totally understand. So, how can we help?
 - Quick order: Through “Order again”, easily find and repeat your previous orders.
 - Special selections: With Chef Leonidas Koutsopoulos, we created the Red Selection – a curated list of restaurants offering something special. We suggest taking a look. Or two. 

• Supermarket
Why go to the supermarket, when the supermarket can come to you? Forget the heavy bags, the checkout lines, and wandering through endless aisles.

Tap on the relevant category on efood and check out efood market — efood’s very own supermarket. Discover your favorite supermarket chains (SKLAVENITIS, AB, My market, Kritikos, BAZAAR, Carrefour and more) and choose whatever you want, at the same prices as in-store.

 - You choose the delivery time: Place your order and pick the day and time that works best for you. Yep, there are supermarkets open on efood, daily, even on Sundays.

 - Don’t miss the deals: Take a look at our awesome prices. 

• Want more? We’ve got you covered!
If you think that we would stop at food, coffee, and supermarkets, think again - we have more! Discover flower shops, liquor stores, pharmacies, greengrocers, butcher shops, fish shops, delicatessens, bookstores, technology products, bio products, optical stores, fitness options, and pet shops. What else do you want? We can bring that too!

 - Forgot a birthday or anniversary? No worries - order flowers, books, or anything else you’d like, and surprise your loved ones with a gift!

- Deals & rewards
Our goal is to help you enjoy everything efood has to offer every single day. Discover how you can make the most of it.

- Become a pro | Free unlimited delivery and 10% off on selected stores.

- Collect rubies, earn coupons | Each order from the same store gets you closer to a coupon for your next one.

- Are you a student? Get ready to eat well! | If you have a student pass, discover unique deals exclusively for you.

Add. Cart. Send.

Τhink it's difficult? Not at all. Trust us! 
 - Step 1: Choose your location
 - Step 2: Pick the store you want
 - Step 3: Add products to your cart
 - Step 4: Cash? Card? Apple Pay? Google Pay? Ticket Restaurant? It’s up to you!
 - Step 5: Send your order

That’s it!

Something went wrong? Check out our FAQ section, or chat with one of our agents.

Available in 100+ cities across Greece
Download the efood app and enjoy anything you want, whenever you want.

On-Demand alcohol delivery with Minibar brings your favorite beers, wines and liquors to the palm of your hands. Minibar Delivery is like having a liquor store on your phone, order your favorite alcoholic beverages for any occasion in just a few taps and we’ll magically deliver it to your door, fast! Download the app to shop the largest selection of wine, beer, liquor, ice, mixers and more at the best prices. Guaranteed.

Download the Minibar Delivery app now and use code: MINIBARAPP for $10 off your first order.

APP FEATURES
=============

> On-Demand Alcohol Delivery: Order for now, or schedule for later. Either way we’ll deliver it fast right to your door.
> Huge Selection: Shop Wine, Beer, Liquor, Mixers, and More from local retailers 
> Best Prices: shop and compare prices to make sure you get the best deal 
> No Hidden Fees: What you see is what you pay, no gimmicks or upcharges.
> Shipping: Not able to order from an on-demand metro? We’ll ship it to you.

WHY YOU NEED MINIBAR DELIVERY

It’s 2022, ordering alcohol online has never been easier? Minibar Delivery will help bring the celebration to you, no matter the occasion. Let the good times roll!

WHERE WE DELIVER

Find hundreds of weekly coupons, deals and other offers. Plus, earn, track and redeem rewards as you shop.

apps.title: RoadWarrior Route Planner
apps.description:
Create reliable multi-destination routes with your trusty copilot, RoadWarrior Route Planner. Designed for drivers, couriers and traveling professionals, RoadWarrior gives you a customized route based on real-time road traffic, client availability, and your own busy schedule.  Last mile drivers and dispatchers can optimize hundreds of stops, customize routes and sync between web and mobile experiences.

Road-tested since 2013 and recently partnered with MapQuest to leverage tremendous capabilities in terms of maps, mapping, routing, fleet management and logistics planning. Join thousands of drivers who save time, money and gas by relying on RoadWarrior Route Planner’s best-in-class optimization and driver-first design.

Who can save time with RoadWarrior?
 
- Professional couriers and delivery drivers: Drivers for Fedex, UPS, OnTrac, DPD, Amazon, logistics managers and many more!
- Flower and gift delivery
- Insurance agents
- Fleet managers and dispatchers
- Sales reps 
- Pharmaceutical sales
- Landscapers
- Realtors
- Food delivery
- Small businesses
- Logistics workers
- Motorcycle trip enthusiasts
- Groups planning a roadtrip 
- Local running groups

Download RoadWarrior Route Planner router now to get started with fast routes. Fleet managers can pair this app with the RoadWarrior Flex web product to manage multiple drivers. 

RoadWarrior Features
- Plan delivery routes with multiple destinations
- Optimize your routes for fast, gas-saving routing
- Navigate using your favorite navigation app such as Apple Maps, Waze, HERE Maps, and more
- Upload addresses in bulk via RoadWarrior’s quick upload tool 
- Even faster address and manifest file upload for FedEx and OnTrac drivers
- Drag and drop your stops to adjust your route in seconds
- Enable “Round Trip” options to create a closed loop in our route planner
- Add availability time windows to arrive at locations during their open or delivery hours
- Track your progress on your route by checking into locations
- Send ETAs to clients on your route with Glympse integration
- Search for addresses from the web, your contacts or simply click on the map

What RoadWarriors Are Saying…

“Lifesaver! Increased my number of deliveries by 40%”

“Off the chain… as a Fedex Ground Contractor, this helps TREMENDOUSLY!”

“I absolutely love this app, as a realtor it has saved me countless hours and gas.”


Route Tracker For Pro Drivers
The RoadWarrior Pro Route Planner upgrade unlocks premium features and increased capacity for optimization and smooth navigation. All the tools and reporting you need for logistics and last mile planning and reporting. 

RoadWarrior Pro is available as two auto-renewable subscriptions:
1) $14.99 USD per month
2) $100 USD per year

Price may vary by location. Subscriptions will be charged to your credit card through your Apple account. Your subscription will automatically renew unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. You can cancel your renewal at any time on this App Store page.

We’ve Got Your Back
Learn more about RoadWarrior Route Planner at: https://support.roadwarrior.app
 
If you encounter any issues or questions, please reach our friendly RoadWarrior customer support team here: support@roadwarrior.app.

For the Geeks (TSP)
RoadWarrior solves one of the most complex challenges known to computer science, the Traveling Salesman Problem (TSP, TSPTW). RoadWarrior elegantly solves the TSP with a custom genetic algorithm specifically tailored for the professional driver/courier. Large transportation and courier companies (FedEx, UPS) have used this type of logistics productivity software for decades to optimize routes for high levels of efficiency. For the first time ever, RoadWarrior makes this powerful TSP software available to iOS drivers.

Privacy Policy and Terms of Use

https://roadwarrior.app/terms-of-service/

apps.title: Deliveries: a package tracker
apps.description:
Deliveries helps you keep track of all your packages, so you always know when they’re going to arrive. Whether it's the latest gadget you've preordered online, or a new graphic novel you can't wait to dive into, Deliveries will keep tabs on it so you don't miss the doorbell.

The main list shows a summary of all your shipments and counts down the days. Select a delivery for more information, and see where it is on a map. If you like you can view the shipping company’s web page, or easily share your shipment over email, iMessage, or AirDrop. Deliveries can even add estimated delivery dates to your calendar, and a Notification Center widget lets you quickly check your packages without opening the app. All your old deliveries are archived so you can look them up again if you need to. An Apple Watch app is also included so you can see the latest updates with just a glance.

Deliveries supports dozens of services, including US Postal Service, DHL, TNT, Canada Post, and many more. You can also track orders from services like Amazon and Apple, even before they ship. (Some services are limited to specific countries—visit junecloud.com/services for details.) If you have packages from other services, just select “Other” and enter a delivery date and web site—so you can check on them when you need to and still keep everything in one place.

Deliveries is also available for Mac. You can sync your deliveries between devices with iCloud or our own Junecloud sync. If you create a Junecloud account, you can add new shipments from any web browser.

Have any questions? Just visit junecloud.com/sync and click Help.

Terms of Use: https://junecloud.com/legal/terms.html
Privacy Policy: https://junecloud.com/legal/privacy.html

raw_data.releaseNotes:
• Fixed missing delivery dates for some Amazon orders.
• Fixed missing status for some Amazon orders, particularly for items that had not shipped yet or were returned.
• Fixed missing items names for Amazon orders when using the Add to Deliveries extension.

apps.title: Bringg Driver App
apps.description:
Bringg is the leading customer-centric logistics solution for enterprises, with customers from more than 
50 countries including some of the world's best-known brands. Using our powerful SaaS platform, companies in the logistics, retail, food, CPG, and services industries can achieve logistical excellence across every aspect of their complex delivery ecosystems while balancing their various needs - from management and marketing at headquarters, through dispatchers and drivers in the field, and all the way to the customers who are at the heart of the entire operation. Bringg provides our customers with strategic value by helping them create optimal delivery experiences and streamline their operations for peak efficiency, all in real-time.
 
The driver app is an integral part of the Bringg platform, providing everything drivers need to efficiently manage their deliveries, completely hands-free:

- Communicate and share location with managers, dispatchers and customers
- Receive tasks and detailed order info and easily navigate to delivery destinations
- Maintain proof of delivery and chain of custody for full control of the supply chain
- Collect barcodes, information, payments, photos, forms, comments and signatures

*Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.

apps.title: Lieferando.de
apps.description:
With the Lieferando iPhone app, you can order the food you love wherever you are in Germany. From over 37,000 restaurants, supermarkets and convenience stores to choose from, you can enjoy everything from burgers, pizza, pasta, sushi, salads and loads more, and get it all delivered to your door.

Need some bits from the supermarket, liquor store or florist? Just open the Lieferando app, choose ‘groceries’ and fill your basket. Whether it’s baby food, diapers, flowers, liquor, beer, wine, beauty products, ice cream, chocolate, milk, fruit and bread, our partners have it all.

How it works:
Ordering is easy. You can either pick a saved address, fill in your postcode/street name or let the app find your location automatically. You can then choose your favourite restaurant or store and select what you fancy. Choose to pay with PayPal, Klarna, credit card, Apple Pay or another option, or pay with cash when your food gets delivered if the restaurant allows it.

Follow your order to your doorstep:
Track your order from the kitchen or store straight to your doorstep with our Food Tracker®. We'll even send you push notifications to update you about the status of your order. It usually takes 30-45 minutes to deliver your food or groceries.

What you get with our app:
- Quick and hassle-free ordering
- Great offers and discounts
- Choose to pick up your order at the restaurant or store
- Re-order the same delicious meal with one tap of a button
- Browse grocery stores, cuisines, offers, best-rated restaurants, nearby spots and vegetarian/halal options
- Get regular updates on your order with our handy Food Tracker®
- Choose from multiple payment options like credit card, PayPal, Klarna and more


Our restaurant partners:
Order from big brands like McDonald’s, Pizza Hollywood, Akakiko, dean&david and Wiener Schnitzelland

Our grocery and convenience partners:
Order from supermarkets and other partners like Spar express.

Let us know what you think
Loving the app? If you have any tips, ideas or feedback, leave us a review or contact us at iosapp@takeaway.com.

Bon APPétit!

apps.title: Tom Thumb Deals & Delivery
apps.description:
Shop, save and plan your meals with our all-in-one app. Get everything you need - from fresh produce and deli orders to pet food and prescriptions - in store or for pickup or delivery. Find and save with weekly deals, coupons and offers. And, easily earn and redeem rewards as you shop. 

With our app, you can:

SHOP EASIER
Quickly add items to your list or cart based on frequent purchases, recommendations and more. View and shop from past orders at any time.

Save with deals & rewards:
Find hundreds of weekly coupons, deals and other offers. Plus, earn, track and redeem rewards as you shop.

Get convenient delivery:
Have your order conveniently delivered to your home - or to your vehicle with DriveUp & Go. Track your order status and get notifications. Check-in curbside to let us know you’re here.

Shop IN Store Mode:
Use the app in store to find items by aisle locations, then scan to check prices and deals.

Create lists:
Make the most of any order or store run by adding items to your shopping list.

Plan meals:
Make sure you get the ingredients you need at the budget you want when selecting from our delicious recipes.

TRY OUR PHARMACY:
Easily manage, transfer, and refill prescriptions for both family and pets. Access vaccines, tests, and consolidate records seamlessly. 

BUILD HEALTHY HABITS:
Monitor your nutrition, steps, sleep, and activities. Earn rewards as you eat better, move more, and stay active. 

Plus, we’re always cooking up new ways to make shopping easier and more enjoyable. Download the app and sign up or sign in with your account to shop, save and plan your next meal.

apps.title: enRoute Delivery Route Planner
apps.description:
enRoute is a smart delivery route planner designed to optimize multi-stop delivery routes for drivers, couriers, and delivery teams. Enhance your delivery process and effortlessly save valuable time, fuel, and effort.

KEY FEATURES:

Fast Address Import
>> Scan Addresses: Using your camera to scan addresses saves time by skipping manual entry.
>> Voice Input: Speak the addresses—perfect for a fast, hands-free setup.

Plan Multi-Stop Routes
>> Optimize over 200 stops, saving time even on the busiest days.
>> Cuts down travel time and fuel costs with intelligent route planning.
>> Maximizes productivity so you can complete more deliveries in less time.

Real-Time Delivery Tracking
>> Track and monitor every delivery from start to finish.  
>> Stay updated on your route’s progress and each delivery's status.
>> Track delays and make adjustments as needed for smooth deliveries.

Live Navigation Notifications
>> Get notified for each upcoming stop—hands-free and on time.  
>> Receive audio alerts, keeping you aware of the next delivery without distractions.
>> Navigation notifications mean no frequent phone checking for directions.

Quick Item Finder Notes
>> Keep items organized with delivery-specific notes.  
>> Add quick notes to each address, ensuring easy access to the right packages.
>> Locate items in seconds, improving efficiency and reducing search time.
>> Keep items organized and avoid delivery mix-ups.

Record Delivery History & Reports
>> Access your complete delivery history and generate detailed reports.  
>> Review past deliveries easily with a full record of routes and deliveries.
>> Export trip data as PDF for organized delivery summaries and reports.
>> Use historical data to enhance future route planning and productivity.

UPGRADE TO PREMIUM: Unlock all features
| Monthly subscription $19.99

Information about the auto-renewal of subscription:
Payment will be charged to iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase.
Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period.
Account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period, and identify the cost of the renewal. The cost depends on the selected plan.
Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user's Account Settings after purchase.
Any unused portion of the free trial will be forfeited when the user purchases a subscription.

Privacy Policy: https://kainsuite.com/privacy-policy/
Terms of Use: https://kainsuite.com/terms-conditions/

apps.title: My Home Delivery
apps.description:
At My Home Delivery we deliver BIG things, on-demand. Nationwide*, same-day and scheduled delivery with unmatched customer satisfaction. We are here to help you with your furniture, home appliances, large item deliveries, and much more using our large, vetted, logistics and trucking companies. 


SAME DAY DELIVERY FOR ALL. From large retail to personal delivery, you can now have items of all sizes delivered on your terms. My Home Delivery is a fast, simple, and affordable way to get things you buy retail or online to where you need it, when you want it. We’re obsessed with customer service and satisfying our customers.


HOW IT WORKS:

1. Get Estimate - enter pick-up and drop-off locations. Tell us what you need delivered. Review rates realtime.

2. Book Your My Home Delivery - Choose your delivery date. You can request a delivery today, or schedule for later. 

3. Get Your Delivery - Keep track of your order every step of the way from pick up to drop off, all in realtime.


HOW WE CAN HELP:

• Ordered something in a retail store that doesn’t fit in the car? We can help! Simply let us know what it is, and we’ll send a sprinter, box truck, or a semi with the right team to get it to your home safe and sound.

• Online Shopping: With My Home Delivery, you can enjoy Prime-style shipping no matter where you shop online.

• Facebook Marketplace & Craigslist: We often let sweet deals go due to lack of delivery options. We got you covered!


WHY My Home Delivery:

• It’s Fast - With My Home Delivery app, you can review rates and schedule a delivery in minutes. 

• It’s Convenient - Book, track, and communicate with your carrier(s) all from within the app. If you run into any issues, we’re here to help. 

• It’s Secured - Know exactly who’s delivering your items. All My Home Delivery carriers have been vetted rigorously with background checks, and backed by a commercial insurance policy.


*We are actively expanding our areas of service nationwide. My Home Delivery currently services the following areas: New York City, Westchester County, Yonkers, Long Island, Greenwich, Connecticut. Stamford, Connecticut, New Jersey, Lawrence, Massachusetts, Franklin Massachusetts, Boston, Massachusetts, Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, Harrisburg, Pennsylvania, Baltimore, Maryland, Aberdeen, Maryland, Brandywine, Maryland, Delaware, Washington DC, Alexandra, Virginia, Indianapolis, Indiana, Chicago, Illinois, Carol Stream, Illinois, Joliet, Illinois, with many more coming soon!


Download My Home Delivery now for all the moving and delivery help you need.


Need help or have a question?

Contact us: support@myhomedelivery.com

apps.title: Blinkit: Grocery in 10 minutes
apps.description:
Blinkit is India’s last minute app. Trusted by millions, it is your everyday online grocery shopping app that home-delivers 10,000+ daily groceries in just a blink. Buy milk products, fresh fruits & vegetables, daily grocery, kitchen, home & office items by shopping for them online on Blinkit. Enjoy easy and smooth app experience with quick delivery.

- Best price and quality fresh fruits & vegetables
- Milk, curd, bread, butter, eggs, cheese, paneer & other daily grocery
- Snacks, biscuits, chips, ice cream, chocolates
- Cold drinks, ice, bottle opener
- Atta, rice, dal, oil, masalas, noodles
- Personal care, detergent, cleaning supplies
- Diapers & baby care
- Pet food
- Bulbs, batteries, mobile chargers
- Emergency medicines, thermometer
- Kitchen tools like chopper, blender, grinder
- Puja needs
- Stationery
- Smart watches, LED lights, Headphones



Beauty & skincare store
Makeup, luxury beauty brands & everyday skincare – now on Blinkit! Shop a huge range of authentic makeup, bath & body, hair care products, beauty accessories & much more!

Electronics store
Wireless or bluetooth earphones? Check. Smart watches? Yes. LED lights? Absolutely! Shop affordable and latest electronics online at best prices, only on Blinkit.

Safe and quick grocery delivery app
The average driving speed for Blinkit (formerly Grofers) delivery agents is 20kmph, since we have a grocery delivery store located every 2 km to instantly serve you.

Many safe payment options
Do your grocery shopping online on Blinkit & pay safely and securely for your groceries with UPI, COD or cards / wallets / netbanking / buy now pay later. We accept Sodexo meal pass and Paytm food wallet too.

Authentic phone accessories
We don’t want you to wait for the most premium and authentic phone accessories out there – which is why you can get them in minutes on Blinkit.

Printouts delivered in minutes
With Blinkit, you can get a printout of anything delivered in just minutes. With convenient options of both black & white and coloured prints, get all your documents sorted instantly!

Low prices, amazing offers
Blinkit (formerly Grofers) offers you big discounts and savings on daily grocery, bundles and bank offers. We give the best prices on online groceries with our monthly House Full Sale!

Live order tracking & helpful customer support
Track your grocery order online, right from your payment being confirmed to the delivery of your groceries. In case you need help, simply tap & chat with our customer support executives who are always ready to assist you.

Delivering groceries in 20+ cities
Instantly do your grocery shopping online! Get delivery of milk, vegetables, bread, snacks & more on the Blinkit app in Ahmedabad, Bengaluru, Chandigarh, Chennai, Delhi, Faridabad, Gurgaon, Hyderabad, Jaipur, Jalandhar, Kanpur, Kolkata, Lucknow, Ludhiana, Meerut, Mohali, Mumbai, Panchkula, Pune, Noida, Ghaziabad, Vadodara & Zirakpur.

Huge variety of local & international brands
Blinkit (formerly Grofers) grocery delivery app has a huge variety of shopping brands available online, including local specialities. In fact, Blinkit has brands you won’t find anywhere else. You can get delivery of daily grocery, festival special products, and even gourmet and international foods! Get the latest products from leading brands like boAt, The Wishing Chair, Ekam, MasterChow, The Body Shop, Farmley, Engage, The Whole Truth, The Moms Co, SuperBottoms, Tropicana, Nestle, Coca Cola, Lay’s, Harvest, Ferrero, Toblerone, Oreo, Nutella, Starbucks, Clinique, Kama Ayurveda, L'Occitane, Innisfree, Davidoff, Rage Coffee, Lindt, Starbucks, Blue Tokai, Sleepy Owl, Wingreens Farms, Bagrry's, Gunsberg, Jade Forest, Jimmy's Cocktails, Eveready, Nivea, Garnier, Lakmé, Haldiram's, Bikano, Heinz, Vahdam, Dettol, Cadbury, ITC, Colgate Palmolive, PepsiCo, Durex, Licious, Aashirvaad, Saffola, Patanjali, Fortune, 24 Mantra, TGL Co., Nestle, Amul, Dabur, & many more.

apps.title: Dolly: Moving & Delivery Help
apps.description:
Dolly is a fast, easy, and affordable way to get the moving and delivery help you need on your terms. Whether you’re moving apartments or you need to get big and bulky items home from retailers like The Container Store, Big Lots, or Crate & Barrel, Dolly delivers. 


DOLLY HELPERS
Dolly connects you to trusted, local professionals with pickup trucks, cargo vans, and box trucks to support your moving and delivery needs. Not only are Dolly Helpers trained to move and handle big and bulky items safely and securely, they’re also background-checked and insured—and all Dollys are backed by our Damage Protection program.


THE MOVING & DELIVERY HELP YOU NEED, ON-DEMAND
* Store Delivery: Convenient, fast, and often cheaper than traditional delivery options
* Mini & Small Moves: The perfect solution for moving one or a few items easily
* Apartment Moves: Dolly will get your stuff safely from A to B
* Labor-Only Moves: For all your heavy lifting needs, get help with rearranging furniture or other large items, just loading and unloading, or even event set-up and tear-down
* Online Marketplace: Get or deliver your Facebook Marketplace, OfferUP, and Craigslist finds
* Donation: Get your big and bulky items picked up and dropped off
* Small Business Moves: Dolly is your alternative to truck and trailer rentals and moving companies
* Storage Moves: Get help loading and unloading your storage unit in one trip
* Junk Removal: Get a hand removing your unwanted items and let Dolly haul it away for responsible disposal


DOLLY IS EASY
Scheduling a move or delivery with Dolly is easy! 

1. Enter your moving or delivery details.
2. Receive an upfront, guaranteed price and schedule a move or delivery that fits your schedule. 
3. Chat with your Helper and track your Dolly progress.


DELIGHTING OUR CUSTOMERS
We’re obsessed with customer satisfaction. That’s why Dolly lets you set the schedule for your move or delivery, find out the cost of your Dolly before you book, and have the peace of mind that your Dolly is backed by our Damage Protection program.

Express24 is a delivery service for your favorite food from restaurants, groceries, and goods from stores and bazaars. Order on App or Web — Express24 courier will bring everything to your door. 

Too lazy to cook? Want to have lunch at the office? Don't want to carry heavy bags? Don't worry, we're here to help. apps.title: Delivery Connect Mobile
apps.description:
Delivery Connect Mobile provides your business, driver and customers with the latest delivery technology.  The driver uses our electronic manifest to assist in the delivery and pickup process by providing driving directions, customer notes, stop notes and verification of orders delivered.  With direct integration with SPOT Notification Center, your driver may communicate with the customer via SMS, Email or by Phone.  Delivery Connect Mobile also provides integration with SPOT messaging and customer search functionality. Delivery Connect Mobile has the option to initiate SMS, Email or Push Notification with delivery, non-delivery and pickup events.  “On demand” and “On the Fly” customer pickup requests are instantly integrated and processed with real-time updates and optimization.

The application uses location services in both foreground and background.  Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.

apps.title: GoShare: Deliver, Move, LTL
apps.description:
GoShare is the best app for finding & booking local delivery & moving professionals on demand. GoShare is one of the largest networks of truck owners, van owners & delivery professionals in the US. Our innovative technology & crowd-sourced model has made us one of the fastest growing businesses in America.

People use GoShare for moving help & delivery services. Moving help includes a truck or van & movers. Businesses use GoShare to improve the last mile & middle mile of their supply chain with our delivery solutions & nationwide network of delivery pros. We support multi-stop routes, hot shot deliveries & offer same day service.

Our fleet of box trucks, pickup trucks, cargo vans, SUVs & sedans allows you to get the right vehicle needed for your project. GoShare delivery pros will load, deliver & unload your cargo. For big & bulky items we recommend selecting 2 delivery pros unless you’re able to assist with loading & unloading.

GoShare makes it easy & convenient to get things done fast. Tell us what you’re moving, where we need to take it & when. We deliver locally or long distance in a truck, van or car that suits your needs at a price that fits your budget. In a few clicks you can book a delivery pro for anything, from a small apartment move to a shipment of pallets. We can deliver small parcels or big & bulky items on demand.

With GoShare you get the best prices, high-quality service & background checked delivery professionals that care about your satisfaction. Our thorough vetting process ensures each delivery pro has the experience necessary to get the job done efficiently & safely.

Track the status of your delivery with real-time notifications & communicate directly with your delivery pro in the GoShare app. After your project is complete, rate your delivery pros & pay through the app. Your ratings & feedback help us build a reliable community of service providers for our valued customers.

Every project booked through GoShare is covered by our comprehensive cargo, liability & auto insurance policies. Say goodbye to long delivery windows, set a time that works for you. Schedule a pickup 7 days a week between 5:00am-11:30pm.

Download the GoShare app to get a fair & transparent upfront price estimate. Request a delivery pro in one minute and save 50% compared to traditional providers. Our app makes it easier than ever to book, track, communicate & pay. White glove service & assembly is available for most items.

Equipment such as a lift gate, dolly, appliance dolly, furniture dolly, lumber rack & more can be requested. Our customer service team is available 7 days a week to help you get moving & answer any questions. Get live chat support from our team in the app or on our website.

Ways people use GoShare:
• Moving Help
• Retail Delivery
• Donation Pickups
• Labor Only Moving
• Facebook Marketplace, Craigslist, Offerup Deliveries
• Furniture Delivery

Ways businesses use GoShare:
• Last Mile Delivery
• Local & Long Distance Freight Shipping
• Courier Service
• Less Than Truckload (LTL) Shipments
• 3rd Party Logistics (3PL)

Industries that use GoShare:
• Retail & Wholesale
• Food & Beverage
• Auto Parts & Equipment
• Construction & Home Services
• Industrial Supply
• eCommerce
• Clothing & Apparel

Currently available in select cities within: Alabama, Arizona, Arkansas, California, Colorado, Connecticut, Delaware, Florida, Georgia, Illinois, Indiana, Kansas, Kentucky, Louisiana, Maryland, Massachusetts, Michigan, Minnesota, Missouri, Nevada, New Jersey, New Mexico, New York, North Carolina, Ohio, Oklahoma, Oregon, Pennsylvania, Rhode Island, South Carolina, Tennessee, Texas, Utah, Virginia, Washington, Washington DC, Wisconsin.

Service not available in every city, but if either the pickup or drop off address is within one of our coverage areas we can accept your delivery request. If we’re not currently available in your city we will be soon, we’re always expanding our services to new areas.

apps.title: Jitsu Drive
apps.description:
Do you want to get paid to deliver packages on your schedule?  Are you looking to make money or earn a side income using your sedan, minivan or SUV?  Do you want to deliver packages but not carry food orders or people?  Jitsu lets you find paid package delivery routes in your area.  You can earn money driving when you want, where you want.

Driving with Jitsu is easy:  Sign up, tell us about yourself and your vehicle, pass a background check, and you can start driving.

Delivering packages with the Jitsu Driver App is easy
- A complete tutorial that shows you how to find delivery opportunities,  pick up routes, complete deliveries, and get paid
- Advance route booking lets you know when and where you'll be driving up to 2 days in advance including guaranteed pay ranges for those delivery routes
- Fast and convenient package label scanning so you can load your vehicle efficiently
- Optimized and flexible routing so you don't waste time or fuel. You can even change the order of delivery stops to fit your schedule.
- Verified drop-off pins and photos so you can be sure you're delivering to the right place
- Ability to contact the customer to get clarifications about the drop-off location
- Real-time support from our Dispatch team (chat or phone)
- Weekly pay with the option to get paid early

apps.title: Snoonu: Food Delivery Service
apps.description:
Snoonu

Snoonu is an online app offering the fastest shopping & delivery services in Qatar, with a variety of restaurants, groceries, retail stores options, and more. 
 
Food Delivery

With Snoonu eating becomes easy - explore restaurant options and order food delivery in just a few clicks.
Find the best deals for fast food delivery like pizza from Papa John’s, Pizza Hut, or Yellow Cab; burgers from McDonald’s, fried chicken from Al Baik, Jollibee, KFC, or sandwiches from Subway.
Snoonu has partnered with thousands of restaurants in Qatar, so we can satisfy your cravings for different cuisines like Japanese, Italian, Filipino, Indian, Kuwaiti, Iranian, Lebanese, healthy, Mexican, vegetarian, seafood and much more. All you need to do? Download the Snoonu app and boost your food mood.
 
Snoonu aims to make your life easier. Get your groceries essentials delivered to your step at no time. Forget about going to a store, staying in line, and carrying heavy bags. Snoonu has your grocery list in one place. Whether you prefer to get your fresh vegetables, meats, and bakery at Almeera, Megamart, SPAR, or Snoomart, you can quickly get your weekly grocery shopping list added to your cart, and check out with any convenient payment method. Snoonu has added Apple Pay as payment option to make your checkout experience even smoother. 
 
Online Shopping

Snoonu is not just an online food delivery app, Snoonu provides you with the online shopping options for pharmacies, electronics, kids toys, flower shops, or any other Qatar retail store you can think about. 
With Snoonu, you can:
Order medication and vitamins from the nearest pharmacy
Surprise your loved ones with flowers or chocolate for any special occasion
Get your kids toys, books, and school supplies without spending hours at the malls
Find the latest releases of electronics and video games 
Plan your weekend adventures and book it online
Snoosend - point-to-point delivery service
 
“Snoosend'' - a new in-app category, enables you to send packages from one location to another within Qatar. You can find the “Snoosend” feature on the home page, place a delivery, select a “from” and “to” locations, write a description of the items, and proceed to check out.


WHY USE Snoonu App?
·     Fastest 24/7 delivery service in Qatar
·     Great offers and discounts
·     Exclusive selection of restaurants and retail stores
·     Online shopping needs all in one place
·     Easy in-app navigation and check-out experience
·     Friendly and responsive customer service team
 
With Snoonu you can:

·     Order fast delivery from anywhere in Qatar
·     Discover local stores, shop online, and get same-day delivery
·     Have 24/7 delivery
·     Track your delivery in real-time
·     Modify your delivery instructions and contact drivers
·     Securely store multiple payment methods
·     Pay by cash or with Apple Pay, Visa, Mastercard
·     Save and name different delivery addresses
·     Rate your experience
·     Find your previous orders and reorder with just a tap
 
Don’t Miss Our Special Deals
Find exclusive deals, discounts, and vouchers by downloading the App. 
Snoonu Red Deals offer a variety of exclusive free delivery and % off deals for food and retail stores options. 
Sign up with your email and phone number and receive special promotions and vouchers.
 
TALK TO US!
We value your feedback and we’ll do anything to make your Snoonu experience exceptional. If you need any help, please contact our customer service at customer.support@snoonu.com

Learn more about Snoonu:                 
·   Our site: https://www.snoonu.com
·   Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/snoonu.qa/

Online Shopping

Snoonu is not just an online food delivery app, Snoonu provides you with the online shopping options for pharmacies, electronics, kids toys, flower shops, or any other Qatar retail store you can think about. 
With Snoonu, you can:
Order medication and vitamins from the nearest pharmacy

Find the latest releases of electronics and video games 
Plan your weekend adventures and book it online

apps.title: Shaw’s Deals & Delivery
apps.description:
Shop, save and plan your meals with our all-in-one app. Get everything you need - from fresh produce and deli orders to pet food and prescriptions - in store or for pickup or delivery. Find and save with weekly deals, coupons and offers. And, easily earn and redeem rewards as you shop. 

With our app, you can:

SHOP EASIER
Quickly add items to your list or cart based on frequent purchases, recommendations and more. View and shop from past orders at any time.

Save with deals & rewards:
Find hundreds of weekly coupons, deals and other offers. Plus, earn, track and redeem rewards as you shop.

Get convenient delivery:
Have your order conveniently delivered to your home - or to your vehicle with DriveUp & Go. Track your order status and get notifications. Check-in curbside to let us know you’re here.

Shop IN Store Mode:
Use the app in store to find items by aisle locations, then scan to check prices and deals.

Create lists:
Make the most of any order or store run by adding items to your shopping list.

Plan meals:
Make sure you get the ingredients you need at the budget you want when selecting from our delicious recipes.

TRY OUR PHARMACY:
Easily manage, transfer, and refill prescriptions for both family and pets. Access vaccines, tests, and consolidate records seamlessly. 

BUILD HEALTHY HABITS:
Monitor your nutrition, steps, sleep, and activities. Earn rewards as you eat better, move more, and stay active. 

Plus, we’re always cooking up new ways to make shopping easier and more enjoyable. Download the app and sign up or sign in with your account to shop, save and plan your next meal.

apps.title: aiqfome: delivery de tudo
apps.description:
Pensou em pedir delivery? Peça pelo aiqfome!

No 2º maior app de delivery do país e líder no interior você encontra os melhores restaurantes da cidade, além de mercados, farmácias, pet shops e muito mais, tudo com cupons e muitas promoções.

E é só pedir que o aiqfome leva até aí rapidinho e você ainda economiza de montão todos os dias. Para pedir é muito fácil: baixe o app, faça seu cadastro e escolha entre as diversas opções. 

Você pode escolher pelas culinárias e pedir delivery de lanche, pizza, hambúrguer, pastel, dentre outros, ou pelo seu restaurante favorito!

Delivery de comida

Seja a sua fome de sushi, marmitex, pizza, hambúrguer ou açaí, o aiqfome tem tudo para acabar com a sua vontade e com aquele preço que cabe no bolso.

Então, se o estômago roncar e a preguiça de cozinhar vir junto, já sabe! É só abrir o app e pedir comida por lá.

Delivery de mercado

Abriu o armário e não encontrou o que precisava? Relaxa, você pode pedir mercado por delivery no aiqfome.

E sabe o melhor? Sem ter que enfrentar filas, se perder nos corredores ou ficar carregando um monte de sacola pesada por aí, porque a gente leva suas compras onde você estiver.

Delivery de farmácia

Imagina estar com dor de cabeça e ainda ter que ir até a farmácia? Ou perceber bem na hora que você vai trocar a fralda do seu bebê que elas acabaram? É, seria um perrengue enorme, se não existisse o aiqfome.

Peça remédios, produtos de beleza e outros itens com cupons e descontos nas farmácias mais perto de você e receba tudo com entrega rápida na porta da sua casa.

Delivery de pet shop

Ninguém fica de fora, nem o seu bichinho de estimação.

No aiqfome você também pode pedir ração, petisco, coleiras, remédios veterinários, caminhas, itens de higiene, areia de gato e muito mais com cupons de desconto nos pet shops da cidade.

Delivery de bebidas

Com o aiqfome, você não precisa nem cogitar deixar a galera ou o churrasco para sair comprar mais bebidas.

Se acabar a cerveja, os petiscos, o gelo ou o que quer que seja, é só abrir o app para pedir delivery e receber em poucos minutos com aquele preço que você AMA (e o seu bolso mais ainda).

Delivery de gás

Quem nunca passou pela situação de estar cozinhando seu almoço a todo vapor e o gás acabar bem na hora?

A situação já é chata por si só, mas ainda ter que ligar para pedir um novo e ficar esperando um tempão para entregar é ruim demais, né?

Ainda bem que pelo aiqfome você resolve essa situação chatíssima em poucos minutos e o seu gás chega antes de bater o desespero.

É delivery de tudo, é rápido e bom para você

Peça agora e tenha a melhor experiência dentre os apps de delivery.

Você pode acompanhar todo o processo do seu pedido, desde o momento em que a loja recebe ele até quando chega aí na sua casa.

E se bater alguma dúvida ou precisar de ajuda antes ou depois de fazer o seu pedido, saiba que você não vai falar com robôs.

O nosso atendimento é feito 100% por humanos preparados e dispostos a te ajudar da melhor maneira possível, não é à toa que chamamos eles de “Ninjas”, é porque eles são bons mesmo.

Cupom de desconto todo dia com o d+, nosso clube de vantagens

Ao assinar o d+, você tem cupons diários de R$10 de desconto ou de entrega grátis para usar em pedidos acima de R$19,99 pagos pelo app em qualquer loja do app.

Além de descontos exclusivos para comprar tudo o que você sempre sonhou no Magazine Luiza, Época, KaBuM! e Netshoes.

Para assinar, abra o app e toque no ícone “Seja d+”!

Para conferir se o aiqfome já chegou na sua cidade, acesse: https://aiqfome.com/cidades

advisories: Infrequent/Mild Alcohol, Tobacco, or Drug Use or References
raw_data.releaseNotes:
olha mais uma novidade fresquinha saindo!
agora ficou muito mais fácil verificar o seu número de telefone (mas com muita segurança rs), se você trocou de telefone ou mudou de conta no app, agora você pode verificar seu número novo diretamente pelo app, sem precisar da ajuda do suporte
ah e se você é novo no app e ainda não verificou, corre verificar para aproveitar todos os cupons disponíveis! confira sempre nossas novidades nas redes: @aiqfome

apps.title: Cargo - Fast, Easy Deliveries
apps.description:
Cargo is a delivery hailing service you can use to have your packages delivered quick and easy.

With the Cargo mobile app, set your package location and destination and have a Courier respond in a matter of minutes. Whatever the size of your package, we will get it there while keeping you informed.

You to your world
Set your pickup and set your destination, and we will handle the rest!

Multi-destination delivery
Send multiple packages to different locations with a single request. One request, one driver, all your packages.

Price estimates 
Not sure what the market price for your trip  should be? With Cargo, you get a price estimate even before you confirm your request.

Stay informed
Receive periodic updates on the status of your package(s) as its being delivered so you can rest easy and stay in control.

apps.title: Ninja - نينجا
apps.description:
Food. Groceries. And more, delivered in minutes!
From your favorite takeout to daily essentials, Ninja is the fastest 24-hour restaurants and grocery delivery service you can count on at the price you want with the variety everyone’s looking for.

Shop better. Eat better. Live better.

Start off with a reward: Love gifts? Get FREE delivery on your first order!
5,000+ Restaurants: Order your favorite cuisine and treat yourself to our daily exclusive offers. 
15,000+ products to choose from: From old favorites and household staples to new restaurants and items you never knew existed, we’ve got it all. And more!
24/7 deliveries: Whether you’re an early bird or night owl, our round-the-clock delivery service will give you what you want when you want it.  
Coffee, tea  & more: Get your daily dose of caffeine delivered and choose from our refreshingly fresh juices, sodas and more. 
Follow your order from the get-go: Track it all from the source to your front door in real time.  
Faster than you can say Ninja: We have our very own riders who’ll  deliver whatever  you order in 30 minutes (or less).
Tap into budget-friendly buys: We’ve got what you want  at the price tag you love! 
Paying is a breeze: We accept all major debit and credit cards and various other payments depending on your location. 

Your favorite cuisines delivered in minutes
5,000+ restaurants choices
Exclusive daily offers on what you crave 

One tap gets you the fastest delivery of grocery! Our diverse product range includes:

Food & drink 
►	Beverages & refreshments: Coffees, teas, juices and a range of mineral water brands.
►	Fresh foods & freshly baked: Fresh meats, poultry, fruits, veggies, bread and baked goods.
►	Dairy & frozen foods: Milk, eggs, cheese, ice creams and frozen meals.
►	Pantry supplies: Oil, flour, pasta, rice, grains and other culinary must-haves. 
►	Health-centric choices: Variety of nutritious and organic snacks, nuts, seeds and more.

Home & you 
►	Baby things: Baby formula, food and care products plus diapers, wipes and more.
►	Beauty Corner: Lenses, lashes, nails, perfumes and specialized skincare and makeup products. 
►	Home cleaning: Cleaning supplies, laundry products and other household staples.
►	Personal care: Personal hygiene, skincare and wellness products.
►	Lifestyle essentials: Electronics and mobile accessories, toys, stationary and other necessary knick knacks. 
►	Fitness center: Protein shakes and bars, gym gear, supplements and other essentials for gym bodies. 
►	Pet care: Nutritious food, toys, grooming products and more for dogs, cats and more.

We’re anywhere you are
Well, that’s the aim! Ninja launched in Saudi Arabia – covering the entire country - and has expanded  its super fast grocery delivery services to Qatar, Bahrain and soon, the  remaining GCC. The reason why we’re doing this? Like you, we like to get things done fast and right. And nothing beats getting delicious food and high-quality buys at lightning speed. 

Experience Ninja for yourself. Download the Ninja App now and get a FREE delivery on your first order!

– Shop online & place an order for pickup or home delivery to skip the trip inside the store!

– To get started, select pickup or delivery from your home screen and use your personalized grocery & shopping lists to start building your cart.

– No membership required, no markup on products, and you can use your mPerks coupons and rewards!

– All your order details are in the Orders section, where you can review, edit, or cancel your order.


IN-STORE SHOPPING

– If you're grocery shopping in-store, remember to scan your mPerks barcode at checkout or link your mPerks to your credit card in the Accounts section so you never have to worry about it.

– Use Shop & Scan to scan items to add them to your cart, clip associated coupons, and skip the checkout line!

– Get organized for making a trip to the store by using the shopping list.


FIND YOUR FAVORITE PRODUCTS

– Explore our selection of grocery products, such as fresh produce, meats, dairy and more.

– Shop our seasonal and holiday collections.

– Stock up on everyday essentials including household items, snacks and more!


REWARDS

– Creating an account automatically signs you up for our mPerks rewards program!

– If you qualify for a reward, we'll start it for you!

– Track your reward progress in the Rewards section and stay up-to-date by opting in to email or push notifications.


COUPONS

– Browse coupons in the coupons section or easily find them as you're building your cart. Find deals in our weekly ad and apply coupons.

– Clip coupons to redeem in store when you enter your mPerks ID at checkout or to have them apply to your pickup/delivery order.

apps.title: Lugg - Moving & Delivery
apps.description:
Lugg: your trusted on-demand moving and delivery service. With just a tap, book your move in as little as 30 minutes or schedule at a time that works for you. With a network of vetted professional movers and a robust multi-million dollar insurance policy, we guarantee peace of mind.

Why Lugg?

• User-friendly: Book a Lugg in minutes.
• Stress-free: Available within the hour.
• Fair Pricing: Get an upfront estimate. No surprises.
• Secure: Vetted Luggers, backed by a multi-million dollar insurance policy.

What can Lugg do?

• Residential Moves: Relocation without the heavy lifting.
• Furniture Delivery: Get your new furniture delivered same day.
• Facebook Marketplace Pick-ups: Score deals without transportation worries.
• Storage Moves: Moving into storage pods or units without the sweat.
• Donation Drop-off: Dust-collecting items? Let us deliver them to charity.
• Junk Removal: Responsible removal and disposal.
• Small Business Moves: Swift assistance for office relocation.
• Labor assistance: Just the muscle for the heaviest lifts.

How it works: Anything moved in 3 easy steps.

1. Book your Lugg: Set your pickup location and destination, select the vehicle that is right for you, and choose a time you would like us to arrive.
2. We'll take it from here: Your Luggers arrive to load your stuff and secure it safely. Track your crew in real time as they head from pickup to the destination.
3. Rate & tip: We unload your items and place them right where you want them, no matter how many stairs or floors. Review your experience and have the option to tip your Luggers for a job well done.

Proudly serving over 7,500 zip codes including major cities like San Francisco, Los Angeles, Seattle, New York City, Boston, Miami, Chicago, Washington D.C., Phoenix, Atlanta, Dallas, Houston, Denver, Sacramento, Portland, Baltimore, Philadelphia, New Haven, and more.
Questions or comments? Email us at support@lugg.com.

raw_data.releaseNotes: We've redesigned the review experience with a streamlined tip and rating interface, making it easier to thank your Luggers and share feedback. This update also includes a fresh new app icon with modern Liquid Glass design and enhanced Live Activities with improved visual elements. Plus, we've updated to the latest platform for better performance and fixed various bugs including display issues on some devices.

apps.title: Mealeo: Takeout & Delivery
apps.description:
Mealeo gives you instant access to your cities best restaurants for delivery or pickup. Whether you're at home, the office, in your dorm, or on a unicorn - we'll deliver straight to you, on-demand. Place your order ahead for pickup and so it's ready when you're arrive. 

If earning Mealeo Moolah (our version of cash back) on every order you place isn't enough to rumble your tummy about downloading our app, here are some other features that will:

YOUR FAVORITE FOODS
Browse menus from restaurants in your city. Choose a familiar favorite or find a new hidden gem. Maybe you want sushi? A pizza? Hot General Tso's Chicken? Whatever it is, we've got it all.

YOUR WAY
Customize your order down to the sauce, spice, or crispy level. Add special requests to your order so the restaurant prepares it just the way you like it.

WHERE YOU WANT IT
Whether you're hungry at home, the office with colleagues, on a unicorn, or your dorm with roommates - we'll deliver straight to you, on-demand. Or, head out for some fresh air and pick it up yourself.

ANYTIME YOU WANT IT
We'll deliver to you whenever you want it - morning, day and night, as long as the restaurant is open to prepare your order. You can even schedule an order up to 7-days in advance, if you're an ultimate planner.

MEALEO MOOLAH
We believe that loyal customers deserve special treatment, so you'll earn Mealeo Moolah on every order you place. Use your Mealeo Moolah for free food and deliveries.

YOUR FAVORITES
Save those gooey mozzarella sticks, that crispy bacon cheeseburger or the spicy pad thai as a favorite in your account, and reorder them with just a few taps.

REAL-TIME TRACKING
Track your order from the moment you submit it, to the moment it goes into your mouth.

EFFICIENT BY DESIGN
In an effort to get your food to you as fast and fresh as possible, a real human assigns your delivery order to the Delivery Partner who can get your order to you the fastest.

REFER FRIENDS; EARN $5 REWARDS
Sharing is caring. Share your personal referral code to send friends $5 in Mealeo Moolah. After they place their first delivery order, you'll receive $5 Mealeo Moolah, magically air dropped into your account.

WAYS TO PAY
Apple Pay, PayPal, Venmo, Debit Card or any major Credit Card.

raw_data.releaseNotes:
Thanks for using Mealeo!

In our latest release:
- Personalized order suggestions
- Enhanced address geocoding for improved accuracy
- Optimized performance for faster and smoother operation
- Improved error handling for greater reliability
- Various bug fixes and stability enhancements

Thank you for your continued support! We hope you love the new look as much as we do.

apps.title: DiDi Rider: Affordable rides
apps.description:
Do you need a ride? Or are you craving a pizza? Ride wherever you want or order food delivery with DiDi, the world's largest mobility app and professional food delivery platform! Order a car in just three taps and travel more relaxed and comfortable. Order delicious food from your favorite restaurants with fast delivery. Download the app and enjoy our special discounts!

Download the DiDi Rider app now and guarantee a quality, economical and safe private transport service. You can also enjoy great food anytime, anywhere. Order your favorite pizza, hamburger, and tacos. A complete app to make your day easier.

DiDi offers these services:

DiDi Express: cheap and safe trip with a qualified driver.

DiDi Economy: cheaper travel, but with the same quality as the DiDi Express.

DiDi Taxi: request a taxi by cell phone to travel more comfortably (available in some cities).

DiDi Delivery: deliver or receive your order, package, or document cheaply.

DiDi Flex: you choose the price of your trip.

DiDi Food: enjoy great food anytime, anywhere.

DiDi Moto: Enjoy better rates and faster rides.

More savings on your travels and safe deliveries

With the DiDi Rider you can travel economically! Order a taxi or a private driver and take cheap trips wherever you want. Do you want a mobility app where you can save money? Then download DiDi Rider!

Food Delivery

Order food from restaurants easily with DiDi! In just 3 simple steps, you can enjoy your favorite delivery without leaving your home.

Your safety is the most important thing

Safe travel first. All DiDi drivers go through a selection process, where only the best are judged. With an extra step of security, you can share your trip in real time with trusted contacts. In an emergency, press the safety button. Travel safely with DiDi!

Choose your payment method

Select the best payment method, credit or debit card, via the app, or cash payment (only available in some cities). DiDi offers discount coupons and exclusive promotions for you to travel cheap. Enjoy it!

Ease of ordering cheap travel deliveries

With DiDi Rider you can travel or order package deliveries with ease. Just enter your current location and destination, and we'll find the nearest private driver or taxi driver. You can see the driver's location in real-time and how long it will take to arrive. Request one of our services, such as DiDi Taxi, to travel cheaply on the largest transport platform in the world!

How to request a trip on the DiDi platform

Download the DiDi Rider app and create an account.

Enter your location and destination.

Select payment method: credit card, debit card or cash payment (available in some cities).

Click "Confirm" and we will find a driver nearby. You will be able to see all vehicle and driver information, including their real-time location and how long it will take to arrive.

Give your opinion at the end of the trip: so that DiDi maintains its quality of service.

With DiDi Rider, you can order safe travel, fast deliveries and enjoy a low fare and a private transfer service with a qualified driver. Also, you can choose to pay cash or card when ordering a cheap trip.

How to request a trip on the DiDi platform

Download the DiDi Rider app and create an account.

Enter your location and destination.

Select payment method: credit card, debit card or cash payment (available in some cities).

Click "Confirm" and we will find a driver nearby. You will be able to see all vehicle and driver information, including their real-time location and how long it will take to arrive.

Give your opinion at the end of the trip: so that DiDi maintains its quality of service.
